INSERT INTO `dialog_message` (`dialog_id`, `message`) VALUES
('agthor0',	'Hello there. Please move along. These things are property of Feygard, and you have no business here.'),
('agthor_guard0',	'Talk to Agthor.'),
('agthor_guard0_1',	'Agthor. Talk to him. *points at Agthor*'),
('agthor_y1',	'Hey, you\'re that kid! That kid that we\'ve been hearing about. It\'s great to finally get a face on the stories we\'ve heard.'),
('agthor_y2',	'Please, anything I can help you with?'),
('agthor_y3',	'Sorry, can\'t help you there. You\'re the only kid I\'ve seen running along here in a long time.'),
('agthor_y4',	'Sure thing. Here\'s what I\'ve got.'),
('ailshara_1',	'Psst, hey. Interested in doing some trading? I am always looking for acquiring.. well, items of others..'),
('ailshara_2',	'Oh yes. You see, these Feygard patrol guards carry some really interesting things. They don\'t seem to care much if some of their shipments.. well, disappear.'),
('ailshara_completed_n_1',	'Sigh, it\'s you. What do you want?'),
('ailshara_completed_y_1',	'Hello again my Shadow friend. How may I help you?'),
('ailshara_deliver_1',	'Hello again. Did you deliver those items to the smith in Vilegard?'),
('ailshara_deliver_2',	'Good. You should also try to convince Gandoren into thinking that you helped him.'),
('ailshara_deliver_3',	'Excellent! You do indeed walk with the Shadow my friend. I am glad to hear that there are at least a few decent folk still around.'),
('ailshara_delivered_1',	'Your help will be most appreciated by the people of Nor City, and you will be welcome among us.'),
('ailshara_fg_1',	'By the Shadow, you sound like one of those deceptive snobs from Feygard.'),
('ailshara_fg_2',	'Shadow help you, child. You should question yourself whether you really are making the right choice here.'),
('ailshara_interested_1',	'Psst, hey you! I saw you talking to Gandoren over there, and I happened to notice that you exchanged some items. Anything interesting?'),
('ailshara_interested_2',	'Hah, of course. Gandoren would not like it if I were to get a glimpse into his business. I assume you are helping him deliver those items somewhere. Tell me this, what did he promise you in return? Gold? Honor? No?'),
('ailshara_interested_3',	'As usual, Feygard keeps all its riches to itself. What if I were to tell you there was a way for you to gain from all this as well?'),
('ailshara_interested_4',	'Let me tell you my plan. As you might know, everyone believes there will be some coming conflict between the deceptive snobs of Feygard and the glorious people of Nor City.'),
('ailshara_interested_5',	'Any help we can bring to Nor City in this matter is welcome. These items that Gandoren gave you would be useful to our people in the southern lands.'),
('ailshara_interested_6',	'These items, if you were to deliver them to our allies down in Vilegard, then the Shadow would look favorably upon you.'),
('ailshara_interested_7',	'This way, the people could get back some piece of the riches that Feygard has stolen from all of us.'),
('ailshara_interested_8',	'If you indeed are walking in the Shadow, then deliver these items to the smith in Vilegard. He will be able to make good use of them. He might also have some other task for you.'),
('ailshara_interested_9',	'Shadow be with you. May the Shadow guide you on the clouded paths that you walk.'),
('alaun',	'Hello. I\'m Alaun. How can I help you?'),
('alaun_2',	'You are looking for your brother you say? Looks like you? Hm.'),
('alaun_3',	'No, I cannot recall seeing anyone by that description. Maybe you should try in Crossglen village west of here.'),
('algangror_1',	'Oh my, a child. He he, how nice. Tell me, what brings you here?'),
('algangror_2a',	'Run away, has he? He he.'),
('algangror_2b',	'Oh sure, you think you can just pick up anything and claim it as yours?'),
('algangror_2c',	'How noble. Maybe you can be of use to me.'),
('algangror_2d',	'Clever. I like that.'),
('algangror_3',	'Tell me, now that you have entered this house, would you be willing to help me with a small.. problem?'),
('algangror_3c',	'Reward? No, no, I don\'t have anything to give you, unfortunately.'),
('algangror_4',	'You see, I have this slight problem with .. ahem .. vermin.'),
('algangror_5',	'Always sneaking around, always trying to cause mischief.'),
('algangror_6',	'Fortunately, I managed to capture some of them, and locked them in my basement.'),
('algangror_7',	'Now, I can\'t handle them myself because of certain .. issues.'),
('algangror_8',	'That\'s where you come in. Would you be willing to .. ahem .. handle those rodents for me?'),
('algangror_9',	'Splendid. Return to me with some proof that they have been dealt with.'),
('algangror_cmp1',	'So, for helping me with the idols, I believe I promised you my enchanted necklace, \'Marrowtaint\'.'),
('algangror_cmp2',	'Wear it well, my friend. Do not let others get hold of the power that Marrowtaint provides.'),
('algangror_cmp3',	'Here you go.'),
('algangror_cmp4',	'Do not underestimate it, my friend.'),
('algangror_cmp5',	'Again, thank you for helping me. You will always be welcome here, friend.'),
('algangror_decline_1',	'Ah yes. After all, you are just a child and I can understand such a task would be too much for you. He he.'),
('algangror_fight_3',	'Jhaeld, the fool. He hides behind his guards and his stone walls. Such a pitiful man he is. Yes, I made those people disappear, but they were all worth it. I will have my revenge!'),
('algangror_fight_4',	'And you, what are you trying to accomplish by running his errands? How fortunate that you entered my house. He he.'),
('algangror_fight_5',	'Do you really think you can defeat *me*? Ha ha, this will be fun!'),
('algangror_remgard_1',	'Oh, it\'s not far from here. Doesn\'t matter really.'),
('algangror_remgard_2',	'You see, I used to live there. To make a long story short, there were some .. ahem .. misunderstandings.'),
('algangror_remgard_3',	'These days, I think they are looking for me, for some reason. Can\'t think of any reason why really. But I believe they are.'),
('algangror_remgard_4',	'Because of our previous .. misunderstanding, I think it\'s best they don\'t find out that I\'m here.'),
('algangror_remgard_5',	'Therefore, I ask of you not to reveal my whereabouts to them.'),
('algangror_remgard_6',	'Thank you. Under no circumstances should you tell them where I am. They will most likely try to persuade you into revealing my location.'),
('algangror_remgard_7',	'Under no circumstances.'),
('algangror_return_1',	'You return. Did you handle all those .. ahem .. rodents in my basement?'),
('algangror_return_2',	'He he. I bet you sure showed them. Excellent. Thank you for .. ahem .. helping me.'),
('algangror_return_3',	'Those rodents have really been bothering me. Good thing I managed to catch some of them. He he.'),
('algangror_return_4',	'Now, there was something else I wanted to talk to you about. Have you been to the city of Remgard in your travels?'),
('algangror_return_c1',	'You return. Thank you for helping me with my .. ahem .. rodent problem earlier.'),
('algangror_return_c3',	'I hope that will teach those *other* rats.'),
('algangror_return_c4',	'Say, you seem like a resourceful person. Would you be interested in helping me with yet another .. task?'),
('algangror_return_d1',	'Oh, it\'s you again.'),
('algangror_return_d2',	'You should probably leave before you tip something over that might .. ahem .. break. He he.'),
('algangror_story',	'Let me tell you my story.'),
('algangror_story1',	'You see, I used to live in the city of Remgard. The times were good, and the city prospered.'),
('algangror_story10',	'So I told myself that others would not hinder me in my curiosity to better myself.'),
('algangror_story11',	'Those books that I bought from the Blackmarrow residence in Nor City - I must have read them all perhaps five times over. This was something completely new to me, and at the same time very exciting.'),
('algangror_story12',	'For some reason, the others in Remgard started giving me strange looks, and I could hear the whispers behind my back.'),
('algangror_story13',	'I was even barred from the tavern. \'People come here for a good time, and we don\'t want people like you here ruining that\' they said. What fools they are.'),
('algangror_story14',	'I heard one woman whispering to her boy, \'Don\'t look at her, she\'ll turn you to stone!\'. Others just turned the other way when they met me.'),
('algangror_story15',	'What fools they are.'),
('algangror_story16',	'One day, Jhaeld showed up at my doorstep with a group of guards.'),
('algangror_story17',	'The people of Remgard had decided that I could not stay there anymore, he said. The things I did were causing other people harm, he said.'),
('algangror_story18',	'What had I done, I asked myself? I had never hurt anyone, much less affected anyone with my .. experiments. Am I not allowed to do what I wish?'),
('algangror_story19',	'I had little chance to argue, however. The guards led me out of the city. They did not even let me gather my things. All my books, all my notes and all my findings - gone. I lost everything.'),
('algangror_story2',	'Our crops grew well, and some people had very fortunate trading agreements with other cities, making the life for most of us living in Remgard very easy.'),
('algangror_story20',	'All this happened several seasons ago. I knew I had to get revenge for what they did to me.'),
('algangror_story21',	'Oh, how I despise them all. The people that gave me those looks, the people that whispered behind my back, and most of all that fool Jhaeld.'),
('algangror_story22',	'So, I decided to extend my .. experiments .. to larger things. To people, to living things. This is the perfect opportunity to learn even more than what is in the books.'),
('algangror_story23',	'To think that I could do it while at the same time get revenge on those despicable people - it\'s an excellent plan, if I may say so myself. He he.'),
('algangror_story24',	'I lured them here. Once I managed to trap them, I placed a curse on them that, in theory, should have only made them unable to speak.'),
('algangror_story25',	'Maybe I haven\'t understood everything correctly from the books that I have read, since instead of making them unable to speak, they were all turned into rats instead.'),
('algangror_story26',	'Practice makes perfect, I suppose. Ha ha.'),
('algangror_story27',	'Oh yes. With your help, they are now one less problem to deal with, so to speak. He he.'),
('algangror_story28',	'So, that\'s my story. Thank you for listening to it.'),
('algangror_story29a',	'Thank you. It is good to know there are more people interested in learning more.'),
('algangror_story29b',	'I never expected you to understand it. No one else seems to understand me either. Oh well, your loss, I guess.'),
('algangror_story3',	'I even sold some of the baskets that I used to make to a wealthy merchant that visited us from Nor City.'),
('algangror_story4',	'However, even the easy life gets boring after a while. I believe it is in our nature to strive for new and better things, to free us from the boredom of day-to-day life.'),
('algangror_story5',	'I wanted to learn more of things that I knew nothing about, and wanted to explore things I had only read of in books before.'),
('algangror_story6',	'So I went to Nor City myself, and visited many .. interesting people and .. dark corners.'),
('algangror_story7',	'Naturally, I was thrilled of the knowledge I gained from the experience, and from what I learned while there.'),
('algangror_story8',	'As I got back home, I wanted to continue practicing what I had observed and learned while in Nor City.'),
('algangror_story9',	'You could say I got obsessed with learning more. I guess the others living in Remgard did not .. share my enthusiasm. Some of them even questioned the fact that I wanted to learn more.'),
('algangror_task2_1',	'Now, I can\'t tell you what task I have in mind before I am confident that you will actually help me. Granted, you have already shown some level of respect for my need of discretion.'),
('algangror_task2_10',	'Remember, it is of utmost importance that you be as discreet as possible about this. The idols must not be found once you have placed them, and no one must notice that you place the idols.'),
('algangror_task2_11',	'So, the first person that I want you to visit is Jhaeld. I hear that he spends most of his time in the Remgard tavern these days.'),
('algangror_task2_12',	'Secondly, I want you to visit one of the farmers named Larni. He lives with his wife Caeda here in Remgard in one of the northern cabins.'),
('algangror_task2_13',	'The third person is Arnal the weapon-smith, that lives in the northwest of Remgard.'),
('algangror_task2_14',	'Fourth is Emerei, that can probably be found in his house to the southeast of Remgard.'),
('algangror_task2_15',	'The fifth person is the farmer Carthe. Carthe lives on the eastern shore of Remgard, near the tavern.'),
('algangror_task2_16',	'Once you have placed these five idols by the beds of these five people, return to me as soon as possible.'),
('algangror_task2_17',	'Again, I cannot stress this enough - you must not tell anyone about these idols, and you must not be seen while placing them.'),
('algangror_task2_18',	'Here are the idols.'),
('algangror_task2_19',	'Now go, and please hurry, we might not have much time.'),
('algangror_task2_2',	'Nor can I describe my reasoning behind this task before you are done with it.'),
('algangror_task2_3',	'Rest assured, you will be sufficiently rewarded by helping me. In fact, you see this necklace here? It has some peculiar powers that many people seek.'),
('algangror_task2_4',	'The world around you seems to move a bit slower when you wear it.'),
('algangror_task2_5',	'As I said, I cannot tell you what task I have in mind, or my reasoning behind it until you are done. I would need your total .. cooperation with this.'),
('algangror_task2_6',	'Good, good.'),
('algangror_task2_7',	'You will tell no one of this task that I am about to give you, and you must be as discreet as possible.'),
('algangror_task2_8',	'I have in my possession five idols. Five idols with very unique .. qualities. What I want you to do is .. deliver these idols to various people in the town of Remgard.'),
('algangror_task2_9',	'You will place them by the beds of five particular persons, and you must hide it well so that the person does not find the idol itself.'),
('algangror_task2_d',	'Very well, return to me once you are ready.'),
('algangror_task2_done1',	'Excellent. Maybe, now I can rest easily. Thank you so much for helping me.'),
('algangror_task2_done2',	'Did anyone see you or where you placed the idols?'),
('algangror_task2_done3',	'Good. Thank you again for helping me.'),
('algangror_task2_n',	'Ah yes. After all, you are just a child and I can understand that all of this must be too much for you. He he.'),
('algangror_task2_n2',	'Can I at least urge you not to disclose my location to the people of Remgard?'),
('algangror_task2_ret1',	'Tell me, how goes the task of placing the idols?'),
('algangror_task2_ret2',	'Please hurry, we might not have much time.'),
('algangror_told_2',	'Say, despite my previous urging to you to keep my location a secret to the people of Remgard, I have this feeling that this trust has been broken. Please tell me it isn\'t so.'),
('algangror_told_3',	'I can feel it in me.'),
('almars',	'He he. They will never know what hit them.'),
('almars_1',	'Oh, hello! Never mind me, I am just strolling along here. Nothing strange about that. See?'),
('alynndir_1',	'Hello there. Welcome to my cabin.'),
('alynndir_2',	'Mostly, I trade with travelers on the main road on the way to Nor City.'),
('alynndir_3',	'Oh, there is not much around here. Vilegard to the west and Brightport to the east.'),
('alynndir_4',	'Up north is just forest. But there are some strange things happening there.'),
('alynndir_5',	'I have heard terrible screams coming from the forest to the northwest.'),
('alynndir_6',	'I really wonder what is up there.'),
('ambelie_1',	'Oh my, a commoner. Get away from me. I might catch something.'),
('ambelie_10',	'Thank you. Now please leave before someone sees me talking to a commoner like you.'),
('ambelie_2',	'I am Ambelie of the house of Laumwill in Feygard. I am sure you must have heard of me and my house.'),
('ambelie_3',	'Feygard, the great city of peace. Surely you must know of it. Northwest in our great land.'),
('ambelie_4',	'Pfft. That just proves everything I have heard of you savages here in the southern land. So uneducated.'),
('ambelie_5',	'I, Ambelie, of the house of Laumwill in Feygard, am on an excursion to the southern Nor City.'),
('ambelie_6',	'An excursion to see if Nor City really is all that I have heard about it. If it really can compare itself to the glamour of the great city of Feygard.'),
('ambelie_7',	'Don\'t you know of Nor City? I will take note that the savages here haven\'t even heard of the city.'),
('ambelie_8',	'I am beginning to be even more certain that Nor City will never, even in my wildest dreams, be comparable to the great city of Feygard.'),
('ambelie_9',	'All the noblewomen in Feygard keep talking about the mysterious Shadow in Nor City. I just have to see it myself.'),
('arambold1',	'Oh my, will I ever get any sleep with those drunkards singing like that?\n\nSomeone should do something about them.'),
('arambold2',	'Sure kid, you may rest here.\n\nPick any bed you want.'),
('arcir_anythingelse',	'Anything else you wanted to ask?'),
('arcir_basement_statue',	'Elythara, mother of the light. Protect us from the curse of the Shadow.'),
('arcir_basement_tornpage',	'You see a torn page from a book titled \'Calomyran Secrets\'. Blood stains its edges, and someone has scribbled the words \'Larcal\' with the blood.'),
('arcir_books_1',	'I find great pleasure in my books. They contain the accumulated knowledge of past generations.'),
('arcir_calomyran_1',	'\'Calomyran Secrets\'? Hm, yes I think I have one of those in my basement.'),
('arcir_calomyran_2',	'Old man Benradas came by last week, wanting to sell me that book. Since it\'s not really my kind of book, I declined.'),
('arcir_calomyran_3',	'He seemed upset that I didn\'t like his book, and threw it at me while storming out of the house.'),
('arcir_calomyran_4',	'Poor old man Benradas, he probably forgot that he left it here. He tends to forget things.'),
('arcir_calomyran_5',	'You looked downstairs but didn\'t find it? And a note you say? I guess there must have been someone in my house.'),
('arcir_calomyran_6',	'What did the note say?\n\nLarcal.. I know of him. Always causing trouble. He is usually in the barn to the east of here.'),
('arcir_calomyran_complete',	'I heard you found it and gave it back to old man Benradas. Thank you. He tends to forget things.'),
('arcir_elythara_1',	'Oh, you found my statue in the basement?\n\nYes, Elythara is my protector.'),
('arcir_start',	'Hello. I\'m Arcir.'),
('arghes_1',	'You will find no business here, child.'),
('arghes_2',	'How interesting. The child from Fallhaven, here in Remgard?'),
('arghes_3a',	'Is that so? Hm, most interesting. It does not change anything, however.'),
('arghes_3b',	'Who I am is of no importance in this situation. You on the other hand, are most important.'),
('arghes_3c',	'I know .. a great deal of things.'),
('arghes_4',	'$playername - yes, that is what they call you.'),
('arghes_5',	'Let\'s just say that I am a .. friend. You would do well to keep your .. friends close.'),
('arghes_6',	'Now, how may I help you? Equipment? Information?'),
('arghes_7',	'Hm, let me see.'),
('arghes_8',	'No, I cannot tell you anything at this time. You are welcome to return once your path has become .. clearer.'),
('arghes_shop',	'Certainly.'),
('arghest_1',	'Hello there.'),
('arghest_10',	'However, now that we guards aren\'t as plentiful as we used to be, it has been a while since I could rest in there.'),
('arghest_11',	'Well, I would like to still keep the option of using it. But I guess someone else could rest there now that I\'m not actively using it.'),
('arghest_12',	'Tell you what, if you bring me some more supplies to keep me occupied here, I guess you could have my permission to use it even though I have rented it.'),
('arghest_13',	'I have plenty of meat here, but I ran out of milk some weeks ago. Do you think you could help me restock my milk supply?'),
('arghest_14',	'Bring me 5 bottles of milk. That should be enough.'),
('arghest_2',	'This is the old Elm mine of Prim.'),
('arghest_3',	'We used to mine a lot here. But that was before the attacks started.'),
('arghest_4',	'The attacks on Prim by the beasts and the bandits really reduced our numbers. Now we cannot keep up the mining activity any longer.'),
('arghest_5',	'I am Arghest. I guard the entrance here to make sure no one enters the old mine.'),
('arghest_6',	'No. The mine is closed.'),
('arghest_7',	'I said no. Visitors are not allowed in there.'),
('arghest_8',	'\'Inn in Prim\' - you sound funny.'),
('arghest_9',	'Yes, I rent it. I stay there to rest when my shift ends.'),
('arghest_return_1',	'Welcome back. Thanks for your help earlier. I hope the room at the inn can be of use to you.'),
('arghest_return_2',	'Welcome back. Did you bring me the 5 bottles of milk that I requested?'),
('arghest_return_3',	'Ok then. Return to me once you have them.'),
('arghest_return_4',	'Thank you my friend! Now I can restock my supply.'),
('arghest_return_5',	'These bottles look excellent. Now I can last a while longer in here.'),
('arghest_return_6',	'Oh, and about the room in the inn - you are welcome to use it in any way you see fit. Quite a cozy place to rest if you ask me.'),
('arnal_1',	'Welcome to my shop. Would you like to see what I have available?'),
('arnal_2',	'(Arnal clears his throat)'),
('arnal_3',	'Welcome to .. *cough* .. my shop. Would you like .. *cough* .. to see what I have available?'),
('arnal_4',	'I don\'t know what .. *cough* .. happened. I started getting dizzy and nauseous. Now this cough is really irritating. It must have been something I ate. *cough*'),
('arnal_bed_1',	'You see a bed and nightstand.'),
