('arnal_bed_3',	'You see a bed and nightstand. This must be Arnal\'s bed.'),
('arnal_bed_4',	'You hide the idol under the bed.'),
('arngyr_1',	'Yes, can I help you?'),
('arngyr_3',	'Oh no, not at all. Go ahead. After all you have done for us here in Loneford, it would be a privilege to be able to give something back to you.'),
('arngyr_4',	'These beds are mostly used by us guards. But I guess I could make an exception since you\'re just a kid. Shall we say, 600 gold and you may use it?'),
('arngyr_5',	'Thank you.'),
('arngyr_6',	'Use the bed in the back over there as much as you like.'),
('arngyr_7',	'Look, kid. I make the rules around here. If that\'s my price then that\'s my price. Take it or leave it.'),
('arngyr_back_1',	'Hello again. I hope the bed is comfortable enough.'),
('askyl0',	'Wh.. who.. Have you come to get me?'),
('askyl1',	'Nooo! I knew the day would come. You people won\'t be able to catch me!'),
('askyl2',	'The Sakul are coming.'),
('atash',	'The Shadow follows us wherever we go. Go with the Shadow my child.'),
('athamyr',	'Walk with the Shadow.'),
('athamyr_1',	'Yes, I have been in the catacombs beneath Fallhaven Church.'),
('athamyr_2',	'But I\'m the only one that both has the permission and the bravery to go down there.'),
('athamyr_3',	'You want to go down in the catacombs? Hm, maybe we can make a deal.'),
('athamyr_4',	'Bring me some of that delicious cooked meat from the tavern and I will give you my permission to enter the catacombs of Fallhaven Church.'),
('athamyr_complete',	'Thanks, this will do nicely.'),
('athamyr_complete_2',	'You have my permission to enter the catacombs of Fallhaven Church.'),
('audir1',	'Welcome to my shop!\n\nPlease browse my selection of fine wares.'),
('aulowenn1',	'Halt! Do not come any closer. The contents of these crates is property of Feygard.'),
('aulowenn10',	'I have two theories. My first thought is that some of the local creatures that we\'ve been having problems with here might have captured them, or even killed them. I know for a fact that some were killed by the creatures, since we even buried some of my men to the east of here, but I am not certain of the others.'),
('aulowenn11',	'The creatures in these woods are intelligible, but fierce. Luckily, we\'ve been able to kill them off before they\'ve been able to spew their foul lies. There are still a few of them around though.'),
('aulowenn12',	'My second theory is that the madman that we are looking for must have done something to them. Maybe the madman has smeared some of his madness onto them.'),
('aulowenn13',	'Regardless, there isn\'t much that I am able to do here. I need to guard these crates.'),
('aulowenn14',	'Also, I do hope that those creatures that seem to live here don\'t return. They\'ve been a real pest.'),
('aulowenn15',	'Oh yes, would you? There is one thing you could do.'),
('aulowenn16',	'As I mentioned, some of my men were killed by the local creatures here. We buried them to the east of here.'),
('aulowenn17',	'I haven\'t been there for a few days now, but last I visited the graves, there was one of those foul creatures standing over the graves.'),
('aulowenn18',	'I\'ve seen that particular creature there before, it seems to be haunting the graves of my fellow men.'),
('aulowenn19',	'Of course, it must be up to no good. I would like your help in either removing or defeating that thing.'),
('aulowenn2',	'I am Aulowenn of Feygard.'),
('aulowenn20',	'Yes, that\'s it. I should also warn you that those creatures are intelligible, so I would urge you to act quickly when encountering it, before it can spew its foul lies.'),
('aulowenn21',	'Good. Return here once you are done.'),
('aulowenn21a',	'Glory to Feygard. Return here once you are done.'),
('aulowenn21b',	'You do as you wish. I\'ll be here regardless.'),
('aulowenn3',	'I\'m guarding these crates. That\'s what I do. At least until my company gets back from their scouting party.'),
('aulowenn4',	'Oh I hope they do get back. Come to think of it, they have been away for quite some time now.'),
('aulowenn5',	'I sure hope they are well. Unlike the others..'),
('aulowenn6',	'In my squad, we were a band of six guards that, together with other squads, were sent out here to find a dangerous madman that takes his refuge somewhere in the nearby hills around here.'),
('aulowenn7',	'But something started to happen once we got here. Some of my fellow guards started acting .. odd.'),
('aulowenn8',	'I don\'t know if was just me imagining things or if something truly happened to them. Anyway, one by one, we started to get fewer and fewer.'),
('aulowenn9',	'Some of my men were killed by the creatures that live in these woods, some ran away by themselves and some have never come back from their scouting trips.'),
('aulowenn_atk0',	'For Feygard!'),
('aulowenn_k0',	'Excellent. Maybe now my brethren can rest peacefully. Thank you so much for helping me.'),
('aulowenn_k1',	'In return, you are very welcome to use my bed to rest whenever you wish.'),
('aulowenn_ms0',	'Hello again. Were you successful in defeating that beast?'),
('aulowenn_tq0',	'You actually listened to it? Please, indulge me, what lies did it have you believe?'),
('aulowenn_tq1',	'Of course we have! They\'ve been attacking us, and we\'ve taken precautions by hunting them so they can\'t kill more of us.'),
('aulowenn_tq2',	'To think that they believe they have a chance against the forces of Feygard. Hah! We will cut them down like sheep once the reinforcements get here.'),
('aulowenn_tq3',	'Hah! Take care of me? That will be the day.'),
('aulowenn_tq4',	'Hah! See, there are those lies that I told you about. They. Attacked. Us. Get it?'),
('aulowenn_wb0',	'Welcome back my friend. Thank you for helping me defeat that foul creature that was haunting the grave of my fellow guards.'),
('ayell',	'You see a pile of bloody body parts.'),
('ayell_1',	'Among the remains, you find a ring with the insignia \'Ayell\'. This must be what\'s left of the former healer of the Charwood hills.'),
('bandit1',	'What have we here? A lost wanderer?'),
('bandit1_2',	'How much is your life worth to you? Give me 100 gold and I\'ll let you go.'),
('bandit1_3',	'About damn time. You are free to go.'),
