('bela_room_3',	'I hope the room suits your needs. It\'s the last room down at the end of the hall.'),
('benbyr_accept_1',	'Splendid!'),
('benbyr_accept_2',	'I happen to know that there are eight of his sheep in total, and they should all be to the northwest of here.'),
('benbyr_accept_3',	'Return to me with proof that you have slain all eight of them.'),
('benbyr_complete_1',	'Hello again. We sure showed that bastard Tinlyn. That should teach him not to mess with me again.'),
('benbyr_complete_2',	'This is a glorious day indeed! Tinlyn should have known not to mess with me!'),
('benbyr_complete_3',	'As for you my friend, seek out my friends in Brightport. I am sure they would extend their hospitality to you.'),
('benbyr_decline_1',	'Very well, but remember that I have my eyes on you.. adventurer.'),
('benbyr_declined',	'I have nothing more to say to you. Leave me.'),
('benbyr_mission_1',	'Ah, my walking accident returns. He he.'),
('benbyr_mission_2',	'Ha ha! That fool Tinlyn must be in tears. The Shadow surely walks with you my friend.'),
('benbyr_story_1',	'Psst, hey. Over here.'),
('benbyr_story_10',	'I want to get revenge on that fool Tinlyn of course. Now, my plan is the following:'),
('benbyr_story_11',	'I have heard that he is herding sheep these days. This is an excellent opportunity for .. shall we say .. an accident to happen to his sheep. He he.'),
('benbyr_story_12',	'You, my friend, would be the perfect walking accident. I want you to find all of Tinlyn\'s sheep and make sure they are forever united with the Shadow.'),
('benbyr_story_13',	'Do this, and I will have avenged that fool Tinlyn.'),
('benbyr_story_2',	'You look like an aspiring adventurer. Are you willing to do some .. (Benbyr pauses) .. adventuring? He he.'),
('benbyr_story_3_1',	'Straight to the point eh? I like that.'),
('benbyr_story_3_2',	'Ah, the adventurer seeks compensation. Tell me, is the thrill of an adventure not reward enough?'),
('benbyr_story_3_3',	'The noble adventurer. He he, I like that. Yes, you will do fine.'),
('benbyr_story_3_4',	'Then I will surely disappoint you. Return to me once you are ready for my task.'),
('benbyr_story_4',	'A while ago, I did some business with a certain man called Tinlyn, over here at this Crossroads guardhouse.'),
('benbyr_story_5',	'As to the nature of our business, I can\'t really tell you. Let\'s just say that our business was of the kind that it was mutually beneficial that the guards did not know about it.'),
('benbyr_story_6',	'We were ready to finish the big deal, me and Tinlyn. That\'s when he decided to turn on me.'),
('benbyr_story_7',	'He reported me to the guards, and made me take the whole blame for our business.'),
('benbyr_story_8',	'I was sent to Feygard prison, while he himself was set free for reporting me.'),
('benbyr_story_9',	'Argh, that fool Tinlyn. I hope the Shadow never shows him any mercy.'),
('birgil_1',	'Welcome to my tavern. Please have a seat anywhere.'),
('birgil_2',	'Well, unfortunately, with the mine tunnel collapsed, we cannot trade much with the outside villages.'),
('birgil_3',	'However, I do have a huge supply of mead that I stocked up on before the mine shaft collapsed.'),
('birgil_4',	'Suit yourself. That\'s what I\'ve got anyway.'),
('bjorgur_1',	'Hello there. You wouldn\'t happen to know anything about a grave to the southwest of Prim would you?'),
('bjorgur_2',	'You have been there?'),
('bjorgur_3',	'My family grave is located in the tomb to the southwest of Prim right outside the Elm mine. I fear that something has disturbed the peace there.'),
('bjorgur_4',	'You see, my grandfather was very fond of a particular valuable dagger that our family used to possess. He wore it with him always.'),
('bjorgur_5',	'The dagger would of course attract treasure hunters, but up until now we seem to have been spared of this.'),
('bjorgur_6',	'Now I fear something has happened to the grave. I have not been sleeping well the last couple of nights, and I am sure this must be the cause.'),
('bjorgur_7',	'You wouldn\'t happen to want to go check on the grave and see what is happening over there?'),
('bjorgur_8',	'Thank you. Please see if anything has happened to the grave, and what could be the cause of my nightly anxiety.'),
('bjorgur_9',	'Please hurry, and return here to tell me of your progress once you find out something.'),
('bjorgur_bandit',	'Hey you! You shouldn\'t be here. This dagger is mine. Get out!'),
('bjorgur_complete_1',	'An intruder? Oh thank you for dealing with this matter.'),
('bjorgur_complete_2',	'You say you restored the dagger to it\'s original place? Thank you. Now I might be able to rest during the nights ahead.'),
('bjorgur_complete_3',	'Thank you again. I\'m afraid I can\'t give you anything except my gratitude. You should go see my relatives in Feygard if you get the chance to travel up there.'),
('bjorgur_return_1',	'Hello again, friend. Thank you for your assistance with my family grave earlier.'),
('bjorgur_return_2',	'Hello again. Have you investigated if anything has happened to my family grave?'),
('bjorgur_return_3',	'Nothing you say? But I was sure something must have happened over there. Anyway. Thank you for checking it for me.'),
