('buceth_10',	'Then, one day, a group of men come walking into the village. Shining armour, white teeth, combed hair, trimmed beards.'),
('buceth_11',	'The men claim that their lord owns this land, including your village.'),
('buceth_12',	'They claim that they keep the land safe of wrongdoers and evil creatures.'),
('buceth_13',	'For their help in protecting your village, they ask that the village compensate them with a share of the harvest.'),
('buceth_14',	'Now, tell me. Would you support those men by agreeing to their terms?'),
('buceth_15',	'How interesting.'),
('buceth_16',	'Let me continue the story of our hypothetical case.'),
('buceth_17',	'A while later, the men return. They explain that some of the methods that are used in the village have now been prohibited across the whole land.'),
('buceth_18',	'Without going into specifics, let\'s say that these are methods that have been used for past generations in your village.'),
('buceth_19',	'Changing the way things are done without these methods will require quite an effort. A lot of people in the village are upset because of this news from the men.'),
('buceth_2',	'Oh, I am sure you do. But what proof do you have, eh? Anything the guards would believe?'),
('buceth_20',	'Now, tell me. Would you in secret continue using the old methods your past generations have used, or would you instead convert to the way that the men are advocating?'),
('buceth_21_1',	'How interesting.'),
('buceth_21_2',	'I am glad to hear that there are people still around that are willing to stand up for what is right.'),
('buceth_22',	'How interesting. You have a different view of the world than what I and the priests of Nor City have.'),
('buceth_23',	'You are of course entitled to your opinion, but you should know that your opinion might conflict with the Shadow.'),
('buceth_24',	'You wanted to know about some business that you accuse me of. Since you have no proof, I will claim innocence. I know that my conscience is clean.'),
('buceth_25',	'Your views match those that I and the other priests from Nor City believe in. Tell me, would you be interested in following the glow of the Shadow?'),
('buceth_26',	'If the answers you gave previously were indeed your views, then I can assure you that the path that is guided by the Shadow is the right one.'),
('buceth_27',	'I am glad to hear that, but then again, I had a feeling all along that you would say that.'),
('buceth_3',	'Let me ask you something first, and we might talk after that.'),
('buceth_4',	'Let me start by telling you a story.'),
('buceth_5',	'Let\'s assume you live in a village that, for the most part, keeps to itself. Your village is self-sustainable and the crops have been good for some years.'),
('buceth_6',	'With the few exceptions of some fights here and there between villagers because of misunderstandings, on the whole, your village is a friendly, peaceful village.'),
('buceth_7',	'You work in the same profession as your parents, which in turn worked in the same professions as their parents.'),
('buceth_8',	'Let\'s also assume that the way you conduct your business is the same way that the people in the village have been conducting their business for generations past.'),
('buceth_9',	'Everyone respects one another in the village, and your appointed leader does a good job at keeping everyone\'s interests satisfied, while at the same time being reasonably fair.'),
('buceth_bribed_1',	'You again. Thank you for the gold earlier.'),
('buceth_complete_1',	'Welcome back my friend. May you bask in the glow of the Shadow.'),
('buceth_decline',	'I am sorry to hear that. I guess we do not share views after all.'),
('buceth_dontknow',	'I am sorry to hear that. You should make up your mind and return to me once you have done so. Then we might be able to talk more.'),
('buceth_fight_1',	'Infidel, you will not defeat me! For the Shadow!'),
('buceth_follow_1',	'Welcome back my friend. Walk with the Shadow.'),
('buceth_gold_1',	'Hm, that might be an interesting proposal. How much gold are you suggesting?'),
('buceth_gold_no',	'Hrmpf. Thanks for the gold, but I am not interested in talking to you. Now, please leave.'),
('buceth_gold_yes',	'You seem to realize the true value of the Shadow. Yes, this will do fine, thank you.'),
('buceth_story_1',	'You wanted to ask me something?'),
('buceth_story_10',	'So, currently, that\'s where we stand now. The deed is done, and the Shadow will look favorably upon us.'),
('buceth_story_11',	'Horrible!? What is horrible? What those people from Feygard are doing - that\'s what\'s horrible!'),
('buceth_story_12',	'Now, I ask you to keep this story just between us two. You understand that, right?'),
('buceth_story_13',	'I urge you to rethink your reasoning. The way of the Shadow is the righteous way.'),
('buceth_story_14',	'Thank you, my friend.'),
('buceth_story_15',	'If you want to learn more about the Shadow, please visit the chapel custodian in Nor City. Tell them I sent you, and they will surely extend their gratitude towards you.'),
('buceth_story_2',	'Let me first tell you my background.'),
('buceth_story_3',	'I am appointed by the priests of Nor City to help guide the people of Loneford towards the Shadow. Our mission is to see that the Shadow casts its glow over Loneford as well as other settlements around here.'),
('buceth_story_4',	'Most folk in these northern parts seem too occupied with obeying the will of Feygard and Lord Geomyr. We want to help people see the light of the wrongdoings that Feygard advocates, and to point out the errors in their ways.'),
('buceth_story_5',	'That\'s my mission here. To see that the Shadow casts its glow over Loneford.'),
('buceth_story_6',	'Nor City sent word to me that something was about to happen here in Loneford. Something that would help our cause.'),
('buceth_story_7',	'They were sending a boy to do some business here, and I was assigned to make sure that the mission was successful.'),
('buceth_story_8',	'I was tasked with gathering samples from the water in the well and from the ground around the well. Also, I was given some vials whose contents should be poured into the well.'),
('buceth_story_9',	'Apparently, the boy they sent was successful in his mission. The task that I did was also successful, if I may say so myself.'),
('bucus_andor_no_1',	'How interesting that you should ask. What if I had seen him? Why would I tell you?'),
('bucus_andor_no_2',	'No, I can\'t tell you. Now please leave.'),
('bucus_thieves_1',	'Who told you that? Argh.\n\nOk so you found us. Now what?'),
('bucus_thieves_2',	'Hah! Join the Thieves\' Guild?! You?!\n\nYou\'re one funny kid.'),
('bucus_thieves_3',	'Ok, tell you what kid. Do a task for me and maybe I\'ll consider giving you more info.'),
('bucus_thieves_4',	'Bring me the key of Luthor and we can talk more. I don\'t know anything about the key itself, but rumor has it that it is located somewhere in the catacombs beneath Fallhaven Church.'),
('bucus_thieves_complete_1',	'Wow, you actually got the key of Luthor? I didn\'t think you would make it out of there.'),
('bucus_thieves_complete_2',	'Well done kid.'),
('bucus_thieves_complete_3',	'So, let\'s talk. What do you want to know?'),
('bucus_thieves_continue',	'How is the search for the key of Luthor going?'),
('bucus_thieves_no',	'Wh, what? No, I don\'t know anything about that.'),
('bucus_umar_1',	'Ok kid. You\'ve proven yourself to me. Yes, I saw some other kid by that description running around here a few days ago.'),
('bucus_umar_2',	'I don\'t know what he was up to though. He kept asking a lot of questions. Kind of like you do. *snicker*'),
('bucus_umar_3',	'Anyway, that\'s all I know. You should go talk to Umar, he probably knows more. Down that hatch over there.'),
('bucus_welcome',	'Hi again, welcome back to the .. Oh wait, I thought you were someone else.'),
('bwm_agent_1_10',	'Good. First though, we must cross this mine to the other side.'),
('bwm_agent_1_11',	'The mine shaft over there *points* has collapsed, so I guess you won\'t make it through there.'),
('bwm_agent_1_12',	'You will have to go through the abandoned mine below. Beware that the mine is pitch-black, so you will have to navigate in there without any light.'),
('bwm_agent_1_13',	'I\'ll try to crawl back through the mine shaft here. That\'s how I got here in the first place.'),
('bwm_agent_1_14',	'Let\'s meet at the other side of this mine shaft.'),
('bwm_agent_1_2',	'We urgently need help from someone outside!'),
('bwm_agent_1_3',	'Very funny. I was sent by my settlement to get help from the outside.'),
('bwm_agent_1_4',	'The people of my settlement, the Blackwater mountain, are slowly being reduced in numbers by the monsters and the savage bandits.'),
('bwm_agent_1_5',	'The monsters are closing in on us, and we desperately need help by some able fighter.'),
('bwm_agent_1_6',	'Reward? Hm, I was hoping you would help us for other reasons than a reward. But I guess my master will reward you sufficiently if you survive.'),
('bwm_agent_1_7',	'Excellent. The Blackwater settlement is some distance away. Frankly, I am amazed that I made it this far alive.'),
('bwm_agent_1_8',	'I must warn you though, that there are some nasty monsters on the way.'),
('bwm_agent_1_9',	'But I guess you seem strong enough.'),
('bwm_agent_1_start',	'Oh, someone from the outside! Please, sir! You have to help us!'),
('bwm_agent_2_1',	'Hello again. You made it through alive, well done!'),
('bwm_agent_2_10',	'It would be your loss. Don\'t say I didn\'t warn you. Safest route would be to head east.'),
('bwm_agent_2_11',	'No no, just head east and I\'ll explain everything to you once we get to the Blackwater mountain settlement.'),
('bwm_agent_2_12',	'Actually, I did tell you that it would be pitch-black down there. Good work navigating through there!'),
('bwm_agent_2_2',	'The Gornauds? I have no idea where they come from, one day they just showed up here around the mountain.'),
('bwm_agent_2_3',	'Nasty beasts, they are.'),
('bwm_agent_2_4',	'Anyway, let\'s get going now. We are now one step closer to the Blackwater mountain settlement.'),
('bwm_agent_2_5',	'We should hurry now.'),
('bwm_agent_2_6',	'Once we exit this mine, it is very important that you go directly east from there. Do not travel to other places other than going east now!'),
('bwm_agent_2_7',	'I\'ll wait for you by the steps up to the mountain pass. See you there!\n\nRemember, go east once you exit the mine.'),
('bwm_agent_2_8',	'Oh, nothing. There are dangerous places here. You should definitely not head any other direction than east.'),
('bwm_agent_3_1',	'Hello. You made it here, good.'),
('bwm_agent_3_2',	'Good. Now let\'s get up this mountain. I will meet you halfway up there.'),
('bwm_agent_3_3',	'This path leads up to the Blackwater mountain settlement. Follow this path and we will talk later.'),
('bwm_agent_3_4',	'Beware of the nasty monsters, they can really cause some harm!'),
('bwm_agent_3_5',	'Do not listen to their lies. They poison your thoughts and would not hesitate to stab you in the back once they get the chance.'),
('bwm_agent_3_6',	'I will not talk of them now. Follow me up to the Blackwater mountain settlement and we will talk more there.'),
('bwm_agent_3_7',	'Indeed they do.'),
('bwm_agent_4_1',	'Hello again. Well done defeating the Gornaud beasts.'),
('bwm_agent_4_2',	'Careful what you wish for, for it may come true.'),
('bwm_agent_4_3',	'Me? There must be something about me that scares them. I have no idea what it would be, some scent perhaps?'),
('bwm_agent_4_4',	'Anyway, we should get going. I\'ll run ahead of you up the mountain.'),
('bwm_agent_4_5',	'Meet me further up the mountain, and we will talk more.'),
('bwm_agent_4_6',	'I do not know where they come from. All I know is that they started to appear one day, blocking the path up the mountain.'),
('bwm_agent_4_7',	'And, their attacks are tough. Once one of them gets a hold of you, the other ones seem really eager to hit you too.'),
('bwm_agent_5_1',	'Hello again. Well done getting through those monsters.'),
('bwm_agent_5_2',	'We are almost there now. Just a little bit more.'),
('bwm_agent_5_3',	'We should hurry this last bit, my settlement is close now.'),
('bwm_agent_5_4',	'I hope you can manage the cold out here.'),
('bwm_agent_5_5',	'Also, stay away from the wyrms. They have a really nasty bite.'),
('bwm_agent_5_6',	'Now hurry. We are almost there. Follow the snowy path to the north, and you should reach the settlement in no time.'),
('bwm_agent_6_0',	'We meet again. Well done fighting your way up here.'),
('bwm_agent_6_1',	'I am glad you followed me up the mountain to help us out.'),
('bwm_agent_6_2',	'Oh yes. In fact, our Blackwater mountain settlement is just down these stairs.'),
('bwm_agent_6_3',	'Go ahead, I will meet you inside.'),
('bwm_agent_6_4',	'You should go down these stairs and talk to our battle master, Harlenn. He can usually be found at the third level down.'),
('bwm_agent_6_5',	'Yes, you seem like an able fighter.'),
('bwm_agent_6_6',	'I learned some shortcuts up and down the mountain a while back. Nothing strange about that right?'),
('bwm_agent_6_7',	'Anyway, we are right at the settlement now. In fact, our Blackwater mountain settlement is just down these stairs.'),
