('celdar_1',	'No, let me guess - you want to know if I have any items to trade?'),
('celdar_2',	'Let me tell you something son. I do not want to buy anything from you, nor do I want to sell you anything. I just want to be left alone here, now that I have made it all the way to this safe haven.'),
('celdar_3',	'I have travelled all the way from my home town of Sullengard, and on my way to Brimhaven, I have stopped at this place to get a break from all the commoners that always bother me with their trinkets and whatnots.'),
('celdar_4',	'So, if you will excuse me, I really need my well deserved rest here. Without you bothering me.'),
('celdar_5',	'Are you still around? Did you not listen to what I said?'),
('chael',	'(Chael gives you a blank stare)'),
('chael_2',	'Chael chop wood. Wood make Chael happy.'),
('chapelgoer',	'Shadow, embrace me.'),
('charwd_guard0',	'You better talk to Maevalia.'),
('charwd_guard1',	'Good. We need all the help we can get.'),
('charwd_guard2',	'I\'ll let you enter the hills. Keep heading east, and then turn north once you see the mountain side.'),
('charwd_guard3',	'Yes, you do that.'),
('charwd_guard4',	'Behind me is the path up to the Charwood mining town. You really should go talk to Maevalia though. She\'s inside the cabin.'),
('charwood_rest',	'Khorailla shouts to you: Hey! Get away from there!'),
('charwoodm',	'Bow before the might of the Thukuzun!'),
('conren',	'We are lucky to have Feygard here helping us.'),
('cr_loneford_st_1',	'Didn\'t you hear? They have all gotten ill.'),
('cr_loneford_st_10',	'I tell you. Savages - that\'s what they are. No respect for the laws or authority.'),
('cr_loneford_st_2',	'It all started a few days ago. As the story goes, someone found one of the farmers passed out in one of the fields, completely white faced and shivering.'),
('cr_loneford_st_3',	'A few days later, the same symptoms started to show on a lot more people.'),
('cr_loneford_st_4',	'Then, all people showed the symptoms in one way or another.'),
('cr_loneford_st_5',	'Some old people even died.'),
('cr_loneford_st_6',	'Everyone started investigating what could be the cause. Currently, the cause is still unknown.'),
('cr_loneford_st_7',	'Luckily, now Feygard has sent patrols up there to help guard the village at least. The people are still suffering though.'),
('cr_loneford_st_8',	'Me, I am certain that this is the work of those savages from Nor City somehow. They probably sabotaged something up there.'),
('cr_loneford_st_9',	'What do they call it, the \'Shadow\'? They are willing to do almost anything to upset the law and order around here.'),
('crossroads_backguard',	'Uh, hello.'),
('crossroads_backguard_1',	'Back there? Oh, nothing.'),
('crossroads_backguard_10',	'Some other guards went in there earlier, and came back screaming. Enter at your own risk, but don\'t say I didn\'t warn you.'),
('crossroads_backguard_2',	'Lead? Oh nowhere. Nothing back there at all.'),
('crossroads_backguard_3',	'Oh no, no. Nothing interesting here. Move along now.'),
('crossroads_backguard_4',	'You would do that? Hm, let me think.'),
('crossroads_backguard_5',	'No.'),
('crossroads_backguard_6',	'No.'),
('crossroads_backguard_7',	'Look, you are not getting back there, and there is nothing to see back there.'),
('crossroads_backguard_8',	'Hm, 800 gold you say? Well, why didn\'t you say so from the start? Sure, that could work.'),
('crossroads_backguard_9',	'I should tell you however, that there is something in there that we won\'t dare go near. I just guard here to make sure it doesn\'t get out, and that no one goes in.'),
('crossroads_guard_1',	'Aren\'t you a bit young to be travelling around here all by yourself?'),
('crossroads_guard_2',	'I sure hope you are not another one of those types trying to sell me your cheap junk.'),
('crossroads_guard_3',	'Go away, kid.'),
('crossroads_guard_r_1',	'Did you hear? Some thieves down in Fallhaven were planning an escape for one of the imprisoned thieves in the prison there.'),
('crossroads_guard_r_2',	'Luckily, someone got wind of it and told the guard captain.'),
('crossroads_guard_r_3',	'It\'s good to know that there are at least a few decent people still around.'),
('crossroads_guest',	'Did you hear about what happened up in Loneford? The guards seem like a bunch of angry bees about it.'),
('crossroads_sleep',	'The guard shouts at you: Hey! You cannot sleep here!'),
('crossroads_sleepguard_1',	'Hello there. Can I help you?'),
('crossroads_sleepguard_2',	'Hello again. I hope the bed is comfortable enough. Use it as much as you like.'),
('crossroads_sleepguard_4',	'No, sorry. These beds are for guards and allies of Feygard only.'),
('crossroads_sleepguard_5',	'Say, aren\'t you that kid that helped the guards down in Fallhaven? With the thieves that were planning an escape?'),
('crossroads_sleepguard_6',	'I knew I had heard about you somewhere. You are always welcome by us guards. You can use that second bed over there to the left if you need to rest.'),
