('duaina_s_2a',	'Cooperating with the thieves in Fallhaven.'),
('duaina_s_2b',	'Working against the thieves in Fallhaven.'),
('duaina_s_3a',	'Something about a dagger returned to an ancestor in a tomb.'),
('duaina_s_3b',	'Something about stealing a dagger in a dark tomb.'),
('duaina_s_4a',	'Killing innocent sheep.'),
('duaina_stop',	'(Duaina stares at you in silence)'),
('dunla_1',	'Me? I am no one. You didn\'t even see me. You certainly did not talk to me.'),
('dunla_default',	'You look like a smart fellow. Need any supplies?'),
('easturlie',	'Hey, this is my house. Get out of here before I call the guards!'),
('elwel_1',	'Go away, I don\'t want to talk to you!'),
('elwel_2',	'(Elwel mutters to herself) Stupid kids ..'),
('elwel_3',	'I saw you talking to that cursed sister of mine. Don\'t listen to her, she always tries her best to portray me in the worst way possible.'),
('elwel_4',	'Now look what you did!'),
('elwyl_1',	'Who are you? Did we invite you here? No, I didn\'t think so. Now get out!'),
('elwyl_10',	'That\'s what I always tell her, to keep it down. She is insistent on shouting at me when we argue. I guess all of her shouting must have made her more or less deaf, since I also have to shout to her to make her understand.'),
('elwyl_11',	'She doesn\'t stop either. I can\'t remember for how long this has been going on, it almost feels like forever.'),
('elwyl_12',	'Oh, my sister is just so stubborn! You know, last night, I was talking to her about those potions that Hjaldar used to make. The smell from his brewing used to reach into our house here.. Or, I mean .. my house here.'),
('elwyl_13',	'So, I was talking to her about those potions of accuracy focus and how I always thought their blue liquid seemed so odd, since there were no blue things that he used while making them.'),
('elwyl_14',	'Then all of a sudden, she started arguing with me about how I have things completely wrong. She insists that the potions were green.'),
('elwyl_15',	'I can\'t understand why she would make such a big deal out of it, when the potion was clearly blue. I remember it distinctly. Argh, how stubborn she is! She wouldn\'t even admit that she is wrong!'),
('elwyl_16',	'Why .. yes .. of course. I am not wrong! They were clearly blue.'),
('elwyl_17',	'Exactly. She is clearly wrong, so why won\'t she just admit it, and we can move along?'),
('elwyl_18',	'Maybe you could go visit Hjaldar and get one of those potions of accuracy focus, and we can both show her that she is clearly wrong.'),
('elwyl_19',	'His house is up on the northeast shore of town. *Elwyl points outside*'),
('elwyl_2',	'Bah. Leave, before I call the guards over here!'),
('elwyl_20',	'I\'m not sure why he doesn\'t make those potions anymore though. Maybe he still has some old ones still in supply that you may have?'),
('elwyl_21',	'Good. Maybe when you bring that potion, she will agree to being wrong for once!'),
('elwyl_22',	'Bah, you kids are never good for anything.'),
('elwyl_3',	'Yes. Argh. It\'s not like I am proud of being a sister to .. her.'),
('elwyl_4',	'She is the black sheep of the family. She never agrees to anything, and always complains. Just look at her.'),
('elwyl_5',	'She even has the stomach to call ME the black sheep of the family, when it is clearly SHE that is causing all the trouble around here.'),
('elwyl_6',	'She\'s always nagging me about how I should move out of what she considers to be HER house, when it in fact is MY house and SHE is the one that should move out so that things can settle down.'),
('elwyl_8',	'Argh. I am so upset at her!'),
('elwyl_9',	'Yes, you can leave! I never invited you here. Leave, before I call the guards!'),
('elwyl_cmp_1',	'Oh, it\'s you again. Thanks for bringing me that potion earlier.'),
('elwyl_pot_1',	'Oh, it\'s you again. What do you want?'),
('elwyl_res_1',	'Oh good. Give me that.'),
('elwyl_res_2',	'Huh, what\'s this? It\'s yellow.. I was sure that it used to be blue. Let me smell it to make sure that it\'s the right kind of potion.'),
('elwyl_res_3',	'Hm, yes, it smells exactly as I remember it. It must be the right potion.'),
('elwyl_res_4',	'This means .. that Elwel was wrong anyway!'),
