('flagstone_brokensteps',	'You notice that this tunnel seems to be dug out from below Flagstone. Probably the work of one of the former prisoners from Flagstone.'),
('flagstone_guard0',	'Ah, another mortal. Prepare to become part of my undead army!'),
('flagstone_guard1',	'Die mortal!'),
('flagstone_guard2',	'What, a mortal in here that is not marked by my touch?'),
('flagstone_guard2_2',	'You seem delicious and soft, will you be part of the feast?'),
