('flagstone_sentry_2',	'You should turn back while you still can.'),
('flagstone_sentry_20',	'A guardian you say? This is troubling news, since it means there is some larger force behind all this.'),
('flagstone_sentry_21',	'Have you found the former warden of Flagstone? The warden used to have a necklace with him at all times.'),
('flagstone_sentry_22',	'He was very protective of it. Maybe the necklace was some sort of key.'),
('flagstone_sentry_23',	'If you find the warden and retrieve the necklace, then please return here and I will help you decipher any message that we might find on it.'),
('flagstone_sentry_3',	'Flagstone has been overrun by undead, and I\'m standing guard here to make sure no undead escape.'),
('flagstone_sentry_4',	'Flagstone used to be a prison camp for runaway workers from when Mount Galmore was dug out.'),
('flagstone_sentry_40',	'You found the necklace? Good. Here, give it to me.'),
('flagstone_sentry_41',	'Now, let\'s see here. Ah yes, it is as I thought. The necklace contains a password.'),
('flagstone_sentry_42',	'\'Daylight Shadow\'. That must be it. You should try to approach the guardian with this password.'),
('flagstone_sentry_43',	'Well, keep looking. Return to me if you need my advice.'),
('flagstone_sentry_5',	'But once the digging in Mount Galmore stopped, the prison camp lost its purpose.'),
('flagstone_sentry_6',	'The lord at the time did not care much for the prisoners that were already in Flagstone, so he left them there.'),
('flagstone_sentry_7',	'The warden that ran Flagstone on the other hand took his duty very seriously, and kept on running the prison just like it was when Mount Galmore was being dug out.'),
('flagstone_sentry_8',	'For years, no one took notice of Flagstone. Except for the occasional reports from travelers of terrible screams coming from the camp.'),
('flagstone_sentry_9',	'There was a change recently, now the undead pour out in great numbers.'),
('flagstone_sentry_return1',	'Hello again. Did you enter Flagstone? I am surprised you actually returned.'),
('flagstone_sentry_return2',	'Hello again. Have you found the former warden in Flagstone yet?'),
('flagstone_sentry_return3',	'Hello again. How is the investigation of the undead in Flagstone going?'),
