('gandoren_11',	'I need you to take a shipment of equipment to another one of our outposts further south on the Duleian road.'),
('gandoren_12',	'Those outposts further down south are in greater need of equipment than us, them being closer to that wretched Nor City and all.'),
('gandoren_13',	'Take this shipment of 10 iron swords to the guard captain stationed in a tavern called \'The Foaming Flask\', near a village called Vilegard.'),
('gandoren_14',	'Bad things? Who have you been talking to then? I would urge you to make up your own opinion of Feygard by travelling there yourself.'),
('gandoren_15',	'Personally, I cannot think of a greater place to be than in Feygard. Order is kept and people are friendly.'),
('gandoren_16',	'As to why you would help us, I can only say that Feygard would be grateful for your services if you help us.'),
('gandoren_17',	'Excellent.'),
('gandoren_18',	'I cannot promise you any amount on a reward.'),
('gandoren_19',	'Ok then.'),
('gandoren_2',	'This guardhouse is a safe haven for merchants travelling the Duleian road. We keep law and order around here, for Feygard.'),
('gandoren_20',	'Here is the shipment that I want you to transport.'),
('gandoren_21',	'As I said, you should deliver those 10 iron swords to the guard captain stationed in a tavern called \'The Foaming Flask\', near a village called Vilegard.'),
('gandoren_22',	'Return to me once you are done.'),
('gandoren_23',	'I feel that I should warn you about something also. See that fellow over there in the corner? Ailshara. She seems very interested in our dealings for some reason.'),
('gandoren_24',	'I would urge you to stay away from her at all costs. Whatever you do, do not speak to her about your mission with the shipment.'),
('gandoren_3',	'Oh sure. Recently, we have had to focus our attention to the troubles up in Loneford.'),
