('gandoren_dr_1',	'Noticed the large road outside? That\'s the Duleian road. It goes all the way from the glorious city of Feygard up in the northwest down to the wretched Nor City in the southeast.'),
('gandoren_noguards_1',	'Hello again. Welcome to the Crossroads guardhouse. How may I help you?'),
('gandoren_rej_1',	'I\'m sorry to hear that. Good day to you.'),
('gandoren_tr_1',	'I\'m sorry, we only trade with allies of Feygard.'),
('gandoren_tr_2',	'I\'m sorry, we only trade with allies of Feygard. Help me with the task I gave you and we might be able to work something out.'),
('gandoren_tr_4',	'Absolutely, as thanks for the help you provided earlier to both Minarra and me, we could agree to trade with you.'),
('gandoren_tr_5',	'Go up in the lookout tower over there and talk to Minarra about equipment. She has our supply.'),
('gandoren_tr_6',	'I hear that Minarra up in the lookout tower over there wants help with something. Why don\'t you go up to her and ask her about it, and we might be able to work something out after that.'),
('gandoren_wantshelp_1',	'Hello again. Welcome to the Crossroads guardhouse. How may I help you?'),
('ganos',	'You seem familiar somehow.'),
('ganos_1',	'Thieves\' Guild? How would I know? Do I look like a thief to you?! Hrmpf.'),
('gauward',	'What.. Oh, a visitor!'),
('gauward_1',	'This place used to be a safe house for travellers between Loneford and Brimhaven, before they had finished the road between the villages.'),
('gauward_2',	'However, nowadays, hardly anyone comes here - because of those cursed creatures from the river.'),
('gauward_3',	'Izthiel, they call them.'),
('gauward_4',	'Ack, if it wasn\'t for those things out there, I am sure a lot of people would come by here more often.'),
('gauward_5',	'Oh sure. I have tried that. But they just keep coming back.'),
('gauward_6',	'Tell you what though. Bring me those claws of theirs, and I\'ll buy them from you for a good price.'),
