('gauward_sold_10',	'Excellent, thank you! Here\'s some gold for your troubles.'),
('gauward_sold_20',	'Oh wow, you managed to get twenty of those claws? That\'s excellent, thank you! Here\'s some gold and some extra health potions for your troubles.'),
