('grimion',	'Hello and welcome to Loneford. Please have a seat, I\'ll be right there.'),
('grimion_rest_1',	'Sure, the guards have set up some beds downstairs. Go talk to Arngyr down there, he might be able to help you.'),
('grimion_trade_1',	'Sure, have a look.'),
('gruil1',	'Psst, hey.\n\nWanna trade?'),
('gruil2',	'Your brother? Oh you mean Andor? I might know something, but that information will cost you. Bring me a poison gland from one of those poisonous snakes and maybe I\'ll tell you.'),
('gruil_andor1',	'I talked to him yesterday. He asked if I knew someone called Umar or something like that. I have no idea who he was talking about.'),
