('guthbered_11',	'We are not sure. But we have our suspicions.'),
('guthbered_12',	'On top of that, there are the attacks from the monsters that we have to deal with.'),
('guthbered_13',	'A while ago, we started seeing the first of the monsters. At first, they were no problem for us to handle. Our guards could cut them down easily.'),
('guthbered_14',	'But after a while, some of our guards got hurt, and the monsters started increasing in numbers.'),
('guthbered_15',	'Also, the monsters almost seemed like they were getting smarter. Their attacks were getting more and more coordinated.'),
('guthbered_16',	'Now, we can hardly hold them back. They mostly come at night.'),
('guthbered_17',	'According to lore, the monsters are called the \'Gornauds\'.'),
('guthbered_18',	'Oh yes, we are almost certain.'),
('guthbered_19',	'Those evil bastards up in the Blackwater Mountain settlement probably summoned them to attack us. They would rather see us perish.'),
('guthbered_2',	'Prim began as a simple camp for the miners that worked in the mines around here. Later it grew to a settlement, and a few years back we even got a tavern and an inn here.'),
('guthbered_20',	'Oh good. Did you talk to Tonis? Yes, I\'m sure you met him on your way into town.'),
('guthbered_21',	'Good. Let me tell you the back-story about Prim first.'),
('guthbered_22',	'We used to trade with them up there, but that all changed once they got greedy.'),
('guthbered_23',	'Oh boy, do we? Yes please, you are welcome to help.'),
('guthbered_24',	'Do you really think you have what it takes to help us?'),
('guthbered_25',	'Great. I think we should go straight to the source with the problem.'),
('guthbered_26',	'A man, from the Blackwater settlement, you say?'),
('guthbered_27',	'Did he say anything about us here in Prim?'),
('guthbered_28',	'That figures. They send out their spies even now.'),
('guthbered_29',	'As I said, we believe those bastards up at the Blackwater Mountain settlement are behind the monster attacks somehow.'),
('guthbered_3',	'This place used to be full of life when the miners worked here.'),
('guthbered_30',	'I want you to go up there to their settlement and ask their battle master, Harlenn, why they are doing this to us.'),
('guthbered_31',	'Thank you friend.'),
('guthbered_4',	'The miners also attracted a lot of traders that used to come through here.'),
('guthbered_5',	'Just until recently, we could at least get some contact with the outside villages. Nowadays, that hope is lost.'),
('guthbered_6',	'You see, the mine tunnel to the south is collapsed, and no one can get in or out of Prim.'),
('guthbered_7',	'You did? Oh. Well, yes of course you must have since you are not from Prim. So there\'s a way through it after all huh?'),
('guthbered_8',	'Ok. We will have to investigate that later.'),
