('irogotu1',	'That whelp Gandir? He was in my way. I merely used him as a tool to dig deeper into the cave.'),
('irogotu2',	'Besides, I never really liked him anyway.'),
('irogotu3',	'NO! You cannot have it. It\'s mine! And who are you anyway kid, coming down here to disturb me?!'),
('irogotu4',	'No. If you want it you will have to take it from me by force, and I should tell you that my powers are great. Besides, you probably wouldn\'t dare fight me anyway.'),
('jan_background',	'Didn\'t you listen the first time I told you the story? Do I really have to tell you the story one more time?'),
('jan_complete',	'Wait, what? You actually went down there and returned alive? How did you manage that? Wow, I almost died going into that cave.\n\nOh thank you so much for bringing me back Gandir\'s ring! Now I can have something to remember him by.'),
('jan_complete2',	'Thanks for dealing with Irogotu earlier! I am forever in debt to you.'),
('jan_default',	'Hello kid. Please leave me to my mourning.'),
('jan_default10',	'I fled and haven\'t dared go back down there because of the critters and Irogotu himself.'),
('jan_default11',	'Oh that damn Irogotu. If only I could get to him. I\'d show him one thing and another.'),
('jan_default11_1',	'Do you think you could help me?'),
('jan_default12',	'Really? You think you could help? Hm, maybe you could. Beware of those bugs though, they\'re really tough bastards.'),
('jan_default13',	'If you really want to help, go find Irogotu down in the cave, and get me back Gandir\'s ring.'),
('jan_default14',	'Return to me when you are done. Bring me Gandir\'s ring from Irogotu down in the cave.'),
('jan_default2',	'Oh, it\'s so sad. I really don\'t want to talk about it.'),
('jan_default3',	'Well, I guess it\'s ok to tell you. You seem to be a nice enough kid.'),
('jan_default4',	'My friend Gandir, his friend Irogotu, and I were down here digging this hole. We had heard there was a hidden treasure down here.'),
('jan_default5',	'We started digging and finally broke through to the cave system below. That\'s when we discovered them. The critters and bugs.'),
('jan_default6',	'Oh those critters. Damn bastards. Nearly killed me they did.\n\nGandir and I told Irogotu that we should stop the digging and leave while we still could.'),
('jan_default7',	'But Irogotu wanted to continue deeper into the dungeon. He and Gandir got into an argument and started fighting.'),
('jan_default8',	'That\'s when it happened.\n\n*sob*\n\nOh what have we done?'),
('jan_default9',	'Irogotu killed Gandir with his bare hands. You could see the fire in his eyes. He almost seemed to enjoy it.'),
('jan_return',	'Hello again kid. Did you find Irogotu down in the cave?'),
('janach',	'This is no place for children. You had better leave.'),
('jhaeld_1',	'What, who are you? Don\'t bother me, child. We don\'t want kids running around in here.'),
('jhaeld_10',	'Ok, so what I would like you to do for me is ask some people what they know of the missing people. The fact that you are not from around here might help you get information that neither me nor my guards would be able to acquire.'),
('jhaeld_11',	'What, you have the arrogance to ask for a reward for helping us find the people that are missing? If it\'s gold you seek, I suggest you look somewhere else.'),
('jhaeld_12',	'I knew you were just trouble. Sigh. Please leave me.'),
('jhaeld_13',	'Why!? It would be the right thing to do, of course. If you can\'t understand that, you had better go somewhere else.'),
('jhaeld_14',	'There are four people here in Remgard that I believe have more to tell than what we have managed to get out of them. I want you to go ask them what they know of the disappearances.'),
('jhaeld_15',	'First, there\'s Norath and his wife Bethir that lives in the farmhouse on the southwestern shore. Bethir is nowhere to be found, and Norath might know more about where she is.'),
('jhaeld_16',	'Secondly, as you might have heard, we have been blessed by a visit from a delegation of the Knights of Elythom here in Remgard. Unfortunately, one of the knights has vanished, which is most embarrassing for us. They can be found here in the tavern.'),
('jhaeld_17',	'Third, the old woman Duaina usually has great wisdom to share, considering the experience she has with .. things out of the ordinary. You\'ll find her in her house to the south.'),
('jhaeld_18',	'Lastly, you should go talk to Rothses, the armorer in town. He meets most people now and then, and might have picked up something that he won\'t dare tell us guards. His house is on the western side of town.'),
('jhaeld_19',	'Please be as swift as possible.'),
('jhaeld_2',	'Hrmpf. I don\'t take threats lightly. Especially not from snot-nosed kids like you.'),
('jhaeld_20',	'As I said, please be as quick as possible.'),
('jhaeld_21',	'What was that? Are you still here? I told you to be as quick as possible.'),
('jhaeld_22',	'Did you not hear me? I told you to be as quick as possible! That means you should go talk to those people instead of standing around here blabbing.'),
('jhaeld_23',	'Are you still talking? I knew you were nothing but trouble the moment I saw you. Now, can you please hurry up and go talk to those people?'),
('jhaeld_3',	'Yes, yes. The missing people. What could possibly a kid like you help with, hm?'),
('jhaeld_4',	'Hm, now that you are here you might as well make yourself useful instead of just standing there looking stupid. Even if you are a kid, you might be able to gather some information for me.'),
('jhaeld_5',	'No, you watch that attitude of yours! Remember where you are and who you are talking to. I am Jhaeld, and you are in Remgard - which could be called *my* city.'),
('jhaeld_6',	'Ha ha. You? Killing something?! Now that\'s about the funniest thing I have heard all day. Just about.'),
('jhaeld_7',	'(Sigh) To even think that we need to get help from children to run errands now.'),
('jhaeld_8',	'I guess you know the background to this situation already. We have had some people disappear on us for some time now. We have no idea what has happened to the people that have disappeared, or even if they are still alive.'),
('jhaeld_9',	'Considering how many there are that have disappeared without anyone knowing what happened, it doesn\'t seem like they are out travelling.'),
('jhaeld_alg_1',	'Hm, yes, and what of it?'),
('jhaeld_alg_10',	'So we forced her to explain herself.'),
('jhaeld_alg_11',	'Would you believe it, she told us that what she believed in, and what she was doing was no concern of ours. She even had the stomach to tell us that she wanted to be left alone.'),
('jhaeld_alg_12',	'Of course, we did what any sane man would do. We forced her to abandon her house and find somewhere else to live. Somewhere other than Remgard.'),
('jhaeld_alg_13',	'You should have seen her. Nails long as your finger, and her face full of unwashed hair. Clearly, she was crazy and could not be reasoned with.'),
('jhaeld_alg_14',	'When we marched her out of town, the children started crying out of fear of her.'),
('jhaeld_alg_15',	'The worst thing though, is that she said she would put a curse on all of us.'),
('jhaeld_alg_16',	'All of this was several seasons ago, and things have gone back to the usual business nowadays.'),
('jhaeld_alg_17',	'Yes. Her being back would explain the missing people. She must have done something to them. I fear for the worst.'),
('jhaeld_alg_18',	'Considering the people that have disappeared, I frankly don\'t know what to do. As you know, even one of the Knights of Elythom has disappeared.'),
('jhaeld_alg_19',	'Someone that can do that is dangerous indeed. I am not sure I would even risk sending the guards out there for her, in fear of what she might do.'),
('jhaeld_alg_2',	'Algangror?! Now that\'s a name I have not heard in a long time.'),
('jhaeld_alg_20',	'If I were to choose, I would rather not deal with it, and just seal the town bridge as safely as possible, to prevent any more people from disappearing.'),
('jhaeld_alg_21',	'I.. I don\'t know what to do.'),
('jhaeld_alg_21n',	'I.. I don\'t know what to do.'),
('jhaeld_alg_22',	'I will not see more of my people get hurt, or whatever it is she has done to them. I will keep my people safe.'),
('jhaeld_alg_23',	'Insults won\'t get you anywhere. The people that have disappeared are still missing, and may be hurt, while you run around handing out insults. I pity you.'),
('jhaeld_alg_24',	'If you really want to help us, then please be careful. She can not be trusted.'),
('jhaeld_alg_25',	'However, if you were to find a way to make her disappear, we would of course be forever in your debt.'),
('jhaeld_alg_26',	'Remember, please be careful! I would not want to be responsible for another person disappearing.'),
('jhaeld_alg_27',	'I doubt it.'),
('jhaeld_alg_3',	'If Algangror is here, this is grim news indeed.'),
('jhaeld_alg_4',	'To be honest, I had heard about this before, but I dismissed all talk of it since I did not believe it. Now you tell me this also, and I am starting to think that it may be true. She may have returned.'),
('jhaeld_alg_5',	'She used to live here in Remgard, during the days of prosperity. She even helped with the crops on some days.'),
('jhaeld_alg_6',	'Then something happened. She started getting ideas, and occasionally locked herself in her house for several days. No one really knew what she was doing in there, but we all knew that she was up to no good.'),
('jhaeld_alg_7',	'I can still recall the stench that came from her house. Ugh. What could possibly smell that bad?'),
('jhaeld_alg_8',	'Anyway, we started questioning her, and tried to persuade her to tell what she was up to. Stubborn and crazy as she is, she refused of course.'),
('jhaeld_alg_9',	'Things started getting worse, and the stench spread like a deep fog over the whole town. All of us living here in Remgard knew we had to act before she did something that could hurt us all.'),
('jhaeld_bed_1',	'You see a bed.'),
('jhaeld_bed_2',	'You see a bed. The idol is still where you left it.'),
('jhaeld_bed_3',	'You see a bed, that you suppose must be Jhaeld\'s bed.'),
('jhaeld_bed_4',	'You hide the idol under the bed.'),
('jhaeld_completed',	'Again, thank you for all your help.'),
('jhaeld_idol_1',	'Please leave me be, child. I just had a sudden attack of nausea. I should probably lie down.'),
('jhaeld_killalg',	'Hello again. What news do you bring?'),
('jhaeld_killalg_1',	'I find this very hard to believe. For to have killed Algangror would have been a difficult task, given her power.'),
('jhaeld_killalg_1b',	'I can hardly believe it! Yes, this is indeed her ring.'),
('jhaeld_killalg_2',	'You actually defeated her? I am so relieved! Tell me, how crazy was she? No, don\'t tell me, I don\'t want to hear more of her filth.'),
('jhaeld_killalg_3',	'This means that the people of Remgard are now safe from her, and it is all thanks to you! Who would have thought.'),
('jhaeld_killalg_4',	'I.. I don\'t know what to say. Thank you, that\'s the least I can say.'),
('jhaeld_killalg_5',	'I would think that the whole town is in your debt, but they may not know it.'),
('jhaeld_killalg_6',	'Go talk to Rothses over at the west side of town. He should be able to help you improve some of your equipment.'),
('jhaeld_leave',	'I think you had better leave, before anything bad might happen to you.'),
('jhaeld_rejected',	'What now? Look, we don\'t want kids like you running around here, messing with our things.'),
('jhaeld_return1',	'Did you talk to those people that I sent you to ask about the missing people?'),
('jhaeld_return2',	'Well, what did you find out?'),
('jhaeld_return3',	'So.. Let me get things straight. You went and asked them about the missing people, and they didn\'t tell you anything new?'),
('jhaeld_return4',	'Oh, I knew you were nothing but trouble the moment I saw you.'),
('jhaeld_return5',	'I sent you to do a simple task, and you return with .. nothing!'),
('jhaeld_return6',	'(Jhaeld mumbles) Stupid kids..'),
('jhaeld_return7',	'Fine then.'),
('jhaeld_return8',	'I suggest you go look in other places if you really want to help us.'),
('jhaeld_task2',	'Maybe someone else knows something that we haven\'t taken into account yet.'),
('jhaeld_task2_1',	'A secret, eh? You would do well to tell me what you know. Lives may be at stake here.'),
('jhaeld_task2_2',	'Ah, someone with honor. I respect that, and will not ask any more.'),
('jhaeld_task2_f',	'Maybe someone else knows something that we haven\'t taken into account yet. Also, I seem to recall you saying something about Algangror before, is that right?'),
('jhaeld_task2_n',	'I have nothing more to say to you.'),
('jhaeld_task2_y',	'Maybe someone else knows something that we haven\'t taken into account yet.'),
('jolnor_chapel_1',	'This is Vilegard\'s place of worship for the Shadow. We praise the Shadow in all its might and glory.'),
('jolnor_default',	'Walk with the Shadow my child.'),
('jolnor_default_2',	'Walk with the Shadow my child.'),
('jolnor_default_3',	'Walk with the Shadow my friend.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_1',	'If you do us a favor, we might consider trusting you. There are three people I can think of that are influential here in Vilegard, that you should try to help.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_10',	'Yes, their reason is to make life miserable for us, I am sure.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_11',	'My reports say that there is a guard stationed outside the tavern, to keep an eye on potential dangers.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_12',	'I want you to make sure the guard disappears somehow. How you do that is purely up to you.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_13',	'It\'s your choice. You can at least go check out the tavern and see if you find anything suspicious.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_14',	'Good. Report back to me when you are done.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_15',	'So, in order to gain our trust here in Vilegard, I would suggest you help Kaori, Wrye and me.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_2',	'First, there is Kaori. She lives up in the northern part of Vilegard. Ask her if she wants help with anything.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_3',	'Then there is Wrye. Wrye also lives up in the northern part of Vilegard. Many people here in Vilegard seek her advice on various things.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_4',	'She recently lost her son in a tragic way. If you can gain her trust, you will have a strong ally here.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_5',	'And last but not least, I have a favor to ask of you as well.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_6',	'North of Vilegard is a tavern called the Foaming Flask. In my opinion, this tavern is a guard station in guise for Feygard.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_7',	'The tavern is almost always visited by the Feygard royal guard of Lord Geomyr.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_8',	'They are probably here to spy on us, since we are followers of the Shadow. Lord Geomyr\'s forces always try to make life difficult for us and the Shadow.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_9',	'Right. Troublemakers indeed.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_return',	'As I said before, you have to help some people here in Vilegard to gain our trust.'),
('jolnor_gaintrust_return_2',	'With your help earlier, you have already gained our trust.'),
('jolnor_guard_1',	'Yes, what about him. Have you removed him yet?'),
('jolnor_guard_2',	'Very good. Thank you for your help.'),
('jolnor_guard_completed',	'Yes, you dealt with him earlier. Thank you for your help.'),
('jolnor_quests_1',	'I would suggest you help Kaori, Wrye and me to gain our trust.'),
('jolnor_quests_2',	'Yes, what about them?'),
('jolnor_quests_completed',	'Good. You helped all three of us.'),
('jolnor_quests_completed_2',	'I suppose that shows some dedication, and that we are ready to trust you now.'),
('jolnor_quests_completed_3',	'You have our thanks, friend. You will always find shelter here in Vilegard. We welcome you into our village.'),
('jolnor_quests_kaori_1',	'You still need to help Kaori with her task.'),
('jolnor_quests_wrye_1',	'You still need to help Wrye with her task.'),
('jolnor_shadow_1',	'The Shadow protects us from the dangers of the night. It keeps us safe and comforts us when we sleep.'),
('jolnor_shop_2',	'I don\'t trust you enough yet to feel comfortable trading with you.'),
('jolnor_suspicious_1',	'Suspicious? No, I wouldn\'t call it suspicion. I would rather call it that we are careful nowadays.'),
('jolnor_suspicious_2',	'In order to gain the trust of the village, an outsider must prove that they are not here to cause trouble.'),
('jolnor_suspicious_3',	'Yes, right. You seem to understand us well, I like that.'),
('jolnor_suspicious_4',	'We have learned from history not to trust outsiders, and you are an outsider. Why should we trust you?'),
('kantya0',	'What will happen to us?'),
('kantya1',	'Thank you for finding our missing people!'),
('kantya10',	'They wanted to find out what was below those markings.'),
('kantya11',	'So they started breaking through further down.'),
('kantya12',	'I wasn\'t there myself, but I heard from some of the miners. As they broke through, there was a rush of air and a clattering noise, almost like claws, coming from the dark hole beneath.'),
('kantya13',	'Below the ground with the markings, there was a cavern, just as they had suspected.'),
('kantya14',	'A foul sulfurous smell crept into the mine, most likely coming from that cavern.'),
('kantya15',	'They started hearing chattering in strange voices from inside the opening.'),
('kantya16',	'Then they saw it. As I\'ve heard it, it all started as a small flame from within the dark cavern.'),
('kantya17',	'The flame grew stronger, and more lights appeared.'),
('kantya18',	'Out of the dark, they came. Out from the depths of the mine.'),
('kantya19',	'Those foul smelling things.'),
('kantya2',	'I told them we shouldn\'t be digging deeper!'),
('kantya20',	'I told everyone that we shouldn\'t have breached that deep. We should have stopped when we first saw those markings on the ground.'),
('kantya21',	'Those markings must have been some sort of warning.'),
('kantya22',	'Yes. Whatever was in that cavern, we should not have let it out. Maybe that way, Morenavia and Ayell would still be alive.'),
('kantya23',	'You\'ve helped us this far. Talk to Maevalia again, she might have something else for you.'),
('kantya3',	'But they did anyway. Now, look what it got us.'),
('kantya4',	'It all started with a few of the miners coming back from their shift. They reported having found some sort of markings on the ground.'),
('kantya5',	'Strange markings. Unnatural. Nothing like we\'ve seen before.'),
('kantya6',	'We don\'t know. No one could make any sense of them, not even Morenavia. I told them all that we should just leave it be.'),
('kantya7',	'But they didn\'t listen.'),
('kantya8',	'Then some people started hearing strange noises coming from below the ground around those markings. Almost like there was something below - a cavern or something.'),
('kantya9',	'Strange noises filled the whole mine, lour rumbles and shrieking noises from within the rock.'),
('kaori_1',	'You are not welcome here. Please leave now.'),
('kaori_10',	'If you really want to prove to me that you are not a spy from Feygard, there actually is something that you can do for me.'),
('kaori_11',	'Up until recently, we have been using special potions made of ground bones as healing. These potions are very potent healing potions, and were used for several purposes.'),
('kaori_12',	'But now, they have been banned by Lord Geomyr, and most use of them has stopped.'),
('kaori_13',	'I would really like to have a few more of those. If you can bring me 10 Bonemeal potions, I might consider trusting you a bit more.'),
('kaori_14',	'Well, hurry up. I really need them soon.'),
('kaori_15',	'Fine. Now please leave me.'),
('kaori_2',	'I don\'t want to talk to you. Go talk to Jolnor in the chapel if you want to help us.'),
('kaori_20',	'Good. Give them to me.'),
('kaori_21',	'Yes, these will do fine. Thank you a lot kid. Maybe you are ok after all. May the Shadow watch over you.'),
('kaori_3',	'He did? I guess you are not all that bad as I first thought.'),
('kaori_4',	'I am still not convinced that you are not a spy from Feygard sent to cause mischief.'),
('kaori_5',	'Hm. Maybe not. But then again, maybe you are. I am still not sure.'),
('kaori_bribe',	'Are you trying to bribe me, kid? That won\'t work on me. What use would I have for gold if you actually were a spy?'),
('kaori_default_1',	'Was there something you wanted to talk about?'),
('kaori_return_1',	'Hello again. Have you found those 10 Bonemeal potions I asked for?'),
('kaori_trust_1',	'I still don\'t fully trust you enough to talk about that.'),
('kaori_vilegard_1',	'You should go talk to Erttu if you want the background story about Vilegard. She has been around here far longer than me.'),
('kaori_vilegard_2',	'We have a history of people coming here and causing mischief. Over time, we have learned that keeping to ourselves works best.'),
('kaori_vilegard_3',	'Anyway, that\'s why we are so suspicious of outsiders.'),
('kaverin_1',	'From the looks of you, you don\'t seem to be from around here. That makes two of us then. He he.'),
('kaverin_2',	'Crossglen! I know that place, it\'s not far from Fallhaven, right?'),
('kaverin_3',	'I have an old .. shall we say .. friend .. from Fallhaven. Goes by the name of Unzel.'),
('kaverin_4',	'You wouldn\'t by any chance have met him, would you?'),
('kaverin_5',	'I guess he keeps to himself. I sure hope he is okay. If you ever run into him, please say hi to him for me.'),
('kaverin_5b',	'Andor? No, I\'m sorry. I\'ve never heard of him.'),
('kaverin_6',	'You?! But.. But.. This is terrible! I bet you are one of the goons of that Vacor fellow.'),
('kaverin_7',	'Excellent, that is good news indeed! May you walk with the Shadow, my friend!'),
('kaverin_8',	'Would you be willing to deliver a message to him?'),
('kaverin_8r',	'My friend from Fallhaven returns. It\'s comforting to hear that Unzel is still alive.'),
('kaverin_9',	'You\'d be well compensated for your efforts.'),
('kaverin_accept1',	'Good, that\'s exactly what I wanted to hear.'),
('kaverin_accept2',	'Make sure this doesn\'t fall into the hands of Feygard, or her loyalists.'),
('kaverin_accept3',	'(He gives you a sealed message.)'),
('kaverin_accept4',	'Good. Now go deliver that message to Unzel.'),
('kaverin_decline1',	'That is unfortunate, you seemed like such a bright boy too.'),
('kaverin_decline2',	'The friend from Fallhaven returns. Please leave me be, I have things to do.'),
('kaverin_done1',	'Thank you, my friend. May you walk in the glow of the Shadow.'),
('kaverin_done2',	'Take this map as compensation for a job well done.'),
('kaverin_done3',	'We\'ve discovered one of Vacor\'s hideouts, far to the south.'),
('kaverin_done4',	'Since you helped us stop him, it\'s fitting that you have this.'),
('kaverin_done5',	'According to the map, the hideout should be just to the northwest of the former prison of Flagstone. Feel free to take whatever is left in there.'),
('kaverin_done6',	'Walk with the Shadow, my friend.'),
('kaverin_done_ret',	'Hello again. It\'s comforting to know that Unzel is still alive, and that you delivered my message to him.'),
('kaverin_fight_1',	'Oh yes, I can feel it. You work for Vacor! He must be stopped!'),
('kaverin_return1',	'It\'s good to see you again. Have you delivered my message to Unzel?'),
('kaverin_return2',	'Please don\'t take too long. Walk with the Shadow, my friend.'),
('kazaul_guardian',	'Kazaul..'),
('kazaul_guardian_1',	'(The guardian looks completely unaware of your presence)'),
('kazaul_guardian_2',	'(The guardian looks down upon you with its burning eyes)'),
('kazaul_guardian_3',	'(You see the burning eyes of the guardian instantly turn into a dark red haze)'),
('keknazar',	'*hssss*\n(You hear squishing sounds as the creature starts moving towards you)'),
('kendelow_1',	'I heard that you helped us get rid of that witch Algangror. Thank you.'),
('kendelow_2',	'Welcome to my tavern. I hope you will find your stay a pleasant one.'),
('kendelow_3',	'Most people here in Remgard tend to their crops. Other than that, I hear that Arnal the armorer over on the western shore has some good business trading.'),
('kendelow_4',	'Also, we usually get a lot of visitors here in the tavern. Lately, it has been a lot fewer people in here though, with the closing of the bridge because of those missing people and all.'),
('kendelow_5',	'On your way in, maybe you noticed that we even have a visit from the Knights of Elythom here in the tavern? It seems that more and more people are becoming aware of the hospitality of Remgard.'),
('kendelow_d',	'How may I be of service?'),
('kendelow_room_2',	'You have already rented my last room. We don\'t have any more rooms other than that one.'),
('kendelow_room_3',	'Why, yes, as a matter of fact, there is. I have one very fine room available upstairs.'),
('kendelow_room_4',	'The previous tenant left in a hurry some days ago.'),
('kendelow_room_5',	'You may rent the room for as long as you like for only 600 gold.'),
('kendelow_room_6a',	'The price is fixed. I cannot go around handing out discounts to just anyone. Also, keep in mind that you may rent it for as long as you wish.'),
('kendelow_room_6b',	'Since you helped us here in Remgard with that witch Algangror, I am prepared to offer you a discount. How about we say 400 gold for it instead?'),
('kendelow_room_7',	'You are welcome to return once you have the gold, if you are still interested.'),
('kendelow_room_8',	'Thank you. The room is upstairs. You may rent it for as long as you wish.'),
('kendelow_shop',	'Oh sure. Here, have a look.'),
