('lodar_find0',	'Oh, it\'s you again. Were you successful in what I asked of you?'),
('lodar_find1',	'Give me that. Oh, yes.. Yes!'),
('lodar_find10a',	'Good.'),
('lodar_find10b',	'Do not forget that you also saved yourself from the Hira\'zinn by defeating it. Had you not done that, it would have crept up on you as well, sooner or later.'),
('lodar_find11',	'I can assure you that my mixtures are .. well .. shall we say .. not for the faint of heart. They can have quite a profound effect on you.'),
('lodar_find2',	'Did you really defeat the Hira\'zinn? It is a formidable foe. I guess you must have, since you gave me its heart.'),
('lodar_find3',	'What was I doing? I was searching for something. I seem to recall you being here before, is that right?'),
('lodar_find4',	'Well, I feel much better now.'),
('lodar_find5',	'Thank you my friend for saving not only me but all of us.'),
