('lodar_find7',	'So, thank you. I am in your debt. Now, how could I repay you?'),
('lodar_find8',	'Maybe you would be interested in purchasing some of my brews, mixtures or herbal salts? I am afraid that is the only thing of any worth that I possess. I will of course offer you a discount.'),
('lodar_forest0',	'I try to keep to myself. Not many people find their way to my cabin here.'),
('lodar_forest1',	'I like that. That way, I am not bothered, like I used to be.'),
('lodar_forest2',	'Oh yes, I too grew up in the city. But that life is behind me.'),
('lodar_forest3',	'Right now, this suits me well. I hope there won\'t be any more .. disturbances, like the one you helped with.'),
('lodar_hira0',	'Ah yes, the Hira\'zinn. It nearly had me fully in its grasp as well.'),
('lodar_hira1',	'That\'s the effects of the Hira\'zinn. Its desires is to consume the minds of all it finds.'),
('lodar_hira10',	'Could that be how the Hira\'zinn extends its reach?'),
('lodar_hira11',	'Yes, that would explain a great deal. The tales speak of it slowly creeping up on the world.'),
('lodar_hira12',	'It could be that those formations are the way it gets closer to the people and things that it wants to consume.'),
('lodar_hira13',	'It could be that the Hira\'zinn has some way of affecting the life of the forest itself, causing these formations to appear.'),
('lodar_hira14',	'That\'s what I think, at least.'),
('lodar_hira2',	'I have only heard of it through tales in books. It has been many generations ago since it last showed itself.'),
('lodar_hira3',	'Last time it crept up on the world, it got its grip on whole villages, I\'ve read. People were fighting their own brethren, after having been consumed by the Hira\'zinn.'),
('lodar_hira4',	'Imagine, sisters and brothers fighting, husbands and wives going at each others throats, all because the Hira\'zinn had twisted their minds.'),
('lodar_hira4b',	'Now, don\'t be so quick to underestimate the Hira\'zinn. It has many tricks up its sleeve.'),
('lodar_hira5',	'I do not know. The tales I have read do not tell how or why it all started - only that there was some kind of conflict going on at that time.'),
('lodar_hira6',	'The wise men during those days also spoke of having seen some sort of signs before things got worse.'),
('lodar_hira7',	'I don\'t know. Something about some rocks turning to life. Sounds like crazy-talk to me.'),
('lodar_hira7a',	'Yes, they might have been.'),
('lodar_hira8',	'Anyway, it\'s good that you defeated that thing.'),
('lodar_hira9',	'Formations of rocks you say? Hm. I don\'t recall seeing any of that the last time I ventured out.'),
('lodar_pots1',	'Oh yes. These are the ones I have available right now. If you want, I can also create some other special potions for you.'),
('lodar_pots2',	'Yes, yes. I have some even more interesting recipes that I might be able to mix for you. However, I am all out of some of the most important ingredients for them.'),
('lodar_pots3',	'If you want me to mix them for you, you\'ll have to help me get those ingredients.'),
('lodar_pots4',	'Yes, were you able to get some of that Spotted Hornbeam fungus from the potion-maker in Fallhaven?'),
('lodar_pots5',	'Oh yes, this will do nicely. Good, good. Thank you, my friend.'),
('lodar_pots6',	'The Spotted Hornbeam fungus is an excellent reagent for creating potent mixtures.'),
('lodar_pots7',	'With your help, I can now create additional potions from the remains of certain animals if you would like.'),
('lodar_pq1',	'Actually, the most important ingredient is the one that I am out of. Most of the potent mixtures that I know of require the spores from the Spotted Hornbeam fungus.'),
('lodar_pq2',	'And that, my friend, is not easy to come by here in the forest. Believe me, I have scoured the nearby forest in search for it, and I have even tried to cultivate some of it myself, to no avail.'),
('lodar_pq3',	'However, I can imagine that the merchants in the larger settlements might have some.'),
('lodar_pq4',	'Yes please. Maybe the potion-maker in that Fall-something town has some? Fall.. brim? Fall.. port?'),
('lodar_pq5',	'Yes, that\'s what I was looking for. Fallhaven. Go visit him and ask him if he has some. I am sure he has some, if you know enough to ask.'),
('lodar_r0',	'Oh, it\'s you again. Now, who were you again?'),
('lodar_spo0',	'With the Spotted Hornbeam fungus that you brought, I can either do a mixture that makes you think you\'re stronger than you actually are, or a mixture that makes you resist attacks more. There\'s also the skin-hardening potion, of course.'),
