('lodar_spo3_0',	'Up in the north, I have heard tales of beast called the Arulir. Their skin is thick as bark due to the interesting oily substance that they produce. I have learned that if you extract some of that thick oily substance, and mix it with an infectious claw from some monster, you can make a potion that makes your skin almost as tough as theirs. I will require two of those skins for it to be effective.'),
