('lodar_xul0',	'No! Get that thing away from me, I want nothing to do with it. I can almost hear the cries of the many lives that that thing has taken.'),
('lodar_xul1',	'I tell you - that thing should be destroyed.'),
('lodar_xul2',	'You should go see the smith in Vile .. haven? Vile .. fall? Argh, I\'m not very good at names.'),
