('maelf',	'Ah, isn\'t this place nice? What else could anyone wish for? This place has all that a man needs - good food, a warm bed and people to exchange stories with.'),
('maelveon',	'[you feel a tingling sensation in your body as the frightening figure begins to speak]'),
('maelveon_1',	'Sssshadow take you.'),
('maelveon_2',	'G.. argoyle Shadow.'),
('maelveon_3',	'A.. llow the Sssshadow in you.'),
('maelveon_4',	'[the figure lifts his hand and points at you]'),
('maelveon_5',	'Sssshadow be with you.'),
('maevalia0',	'You there! This is no place for children!'),
('maevalia1',	'The Charwood area has become a dangerous place as of late. You should leave at once unless you want to get killed .. or worse.'),
('maevalia10',	'Our mining town up in the Charwood hills is completely overrun, however. All our belongings are back there.'),
('maevalia11',	'There are also several of us that haven\'t made it down the hill. Many of our friends and relatives from the mining town have not been accounted for yet.'),
('maevalia12',	'I don\'t want to think about that. Either they\'ve been killed by the foul monsters, or worse.'),
('maevalia13',	'You know, we saw one monster carrying around what looked like a net of some sort, instead of weapons like the other ones.'),
('maevalia14',	'He shoved the other monsters around, and they all seemed to look up to him, like he was some sort of leader.'),
('maevalia15',	'I don\'t know what that net was for though. I wonder if he was supposed to capture some of us.'),
('maevalia16',	'I sure hope that the people that we are missing are all alive at least.'),
('maevalia17',	'In particular, I\'m worried about what happened to Morenavia - our leader. None of us that made it back to this cabin saw what happened to her.'),
('maevalia18',	'I sure hope she\'s still alive. We could use some of her wisdom and leadership right now to guide us.'),
('maevalia19',	'I\'m also worried about Falothen, our weapons trainer. As I ran down the hills myself, I thought I heard him call for help.'),
('maevalia2',	'For your sake, I urge you to leave. While we need all the help we can get, we can\'t take responsibility for the dangers that has befell our mining town of Charwood.'),
('maevalia20',	'There\'s also Ayell, our healer, and Fayvara, our armorer. They always stayed together, those two. We don\'t know what happened to them or where they are.'),
('maevalia21',	'I honestly don\'t know. We\'ve sent out runners to try to find help. So far, none have returned with help.'),
('maevalia21a',	'With your help, we might at least get somewhere.'),
('maevalia22',	'Yes, I guess so. Thank you for listening to our story.'),
('maevalia23',	'Well, I wouldn\'t want to be responsible for putting you into any trouble.'),
('maevalia24',	'Ok. Frankly, I don\'t know what else we can do. We really need the help.'),
('maevalia25',	'I would be very grateful for knowing what happened to the people we are missing.'),
('maevalia26',	'Head up to our mining town of Charwood heights, and look for the missing people.'),
('maevalia27',	'Please, try to be safe! If you spot any danger, or if those foul monsters are too much for you, don\'t hesitate to retreat back here.'),
('maevalia28',	'Thank you. The path up to Charwood heights is just east of here.'),
('maevalia3',	'We were attacked. We didn\'t stand a chance, they were too many and we are no fighters.'),
('maevalia4',	'They started pouring out of the mine and the surrounding hills.'),
('maevalia5',	'The monsters. Disgusting, foul smelling monsters. Nothing like we\'ve ever seen before.'),
('maevalia6',	'They ransacked our whole mining camp. Even burnt down the wooden carving that Morenavia had created last year.'),
('maevalia7',	'We did the only thing we can, seeing as none of us were equipped to fight. We ran.'),
('maevalia8',	'We ran down the mountain, leaving behind our mining settlement of Charwood. Some of us made it here to our former cabin.'),
('maevalia9',	'The few of us that\'s left have been able to hold them off from here, at least for now.'),
('maevalia_d1',	'It\'s good to see that Falothen and Fayvara are well. Anything else that I can help you with?'),
('maevalia_d10',	'Thank you.'),
('maevalia_d2',	'Absolutely. Pick any bed you want over there.'),
('maevalia_d3',	'I have my guesses. Go talk to Kantya about it. I hear she has the full story, and some interesting theories.'),
('maevalia_d4',	'Good. Did she tell you about that marking on the ground? I saw it myself. Nothing like I\'ve ever seen before.'),
('maevalia_d5',	'I wonder what is down there, in the deeper parts of the mine. I bet that whatever is controlling those monsters is still down there.'),
('maevalia_d6',	'Can\'t say I blame you. Thank you for the help you\'ve provided so far.'),
('maevalia_d7',	'You would do that for us? Thank you. I don\'t know what we would do without your help.'),
('maevalia_d8',	'Please try to be safe, and be on the lookout for the dangerous monsters that inhabit the mine.'),
('maevalia_d9',	'Whatever lurks down there, I\'m sure it\'s not happy to get any visitors.'),
('maevalia_h10',	'Certainly. Here is what we can spare. Thank you yet again.'),
('maevalia_h11',	'After helping us, you still want to deprive us of more things that we cherish?'),
('maevalia_h12',	'I guess we have no choice but to agree. Here, take these. They used to belong to my mother.'),
('maevalia_h2',	'Hello again. Did you reach the lower parts of the Charwood mine?'),
('maevalia_h3',	'None of us ever dared to venture that deep.'),
('maevalia_h5',	'You actually killed it?'),
('maevalia_h6',	'You are truly a hero to us.'),
('maevalia_h7',	'Not only did you manage to find our missing people, but you also freed us from the creature that caused all this trouble.'),
('maevalia_h8',	'We are forever in your debt. What can we do to ever repay you?'),
('maevalia_h9',	'You are truly our hero. Thank you yet again.'),
('maevalia_q1',	'Thank you for all your help!'),
('maevalia_r0',	'You again.'),
('maevalia_r1',	'Hello again. Did you find our missing people?'),
('maevalia_r10',	'Good. We are truly grateful for the help that you have provided to us from the Charwood heights.'),
('maevalia_r3',	'Yes, what about them?'),
('maevalia_r3b',	'Thank you for helping us.'),
('maevalia_r4',	'Yes, what about them? I saw that Falothen and Fayvara have returned.'),
('maevalia_r5',	'While I am very happy to hear that Falothen and Fayvara are alive and well, it saddens me to hear that we\'ve lost not only Ayell, but also Morenavia.'),
('maevalia_r6',	'Morenavia was truly a great leader for us. Now, how will we ever be able to find the right paths?'),
('maevalia_r7',	'Things will never be the same again for us.'),
('maevalia_r8',	'It is at least some comfort to know that we still have Falothen and Fayvara with us.'),
('maevalia_r9',	'I hear they are both anxious to talk to you now that they\'re safe. You should go meet them downstairs in the basement.'),
