('mikhail3',	'Never mind, he will probably be back soon.'),
('mikhail_andor1',	'As I said, Andor went out yesterday and hasn\'t been back since. I\'m starting to worry about him. Please go look for your brother, he said he would only be out a short while.'),
('mikhail_andor2',	'Maybe he went into that supply cave again and got stuck. Or maybe he\'s in Leta\'s basement training with that wooden sword again. Please go look for him in town.'),
