('narael',	'Thank you, thank you for freeing me from that monster.'),
('narael_1',	'I have been a captive here for what seems to be an eternity.'),
('narael_2',	'Oh, the things they did to me. Thank you so much for freeing me.'),
('narael_3',	'I was once a citizen in Nor City, and worked on the excavation of Mount Galmore.'),
('narael_4',	'After a while, the day came when I wanted to quit the assignment and return to my wife.'),
('narael_5',	'The officer in charge would not let me, and I was sent to Flagstone as a prisoner for disobeying orders.'),
('narael_6',	'If only I could see my wife once more. I have hardly any life left in me, and I don\'t even have enough strength to leave this place.'),
('narael_7',	'I guess my fate is to perish here, but now as a free man at least.'),
('narael_8',	'Now leave me to my fate. I do not have the strength to leave this place.'),
('narael_9',	'If you find my wife Taurum in Nor City, please tell her I\'m alive and that I haven\'t forgotten about her.'),
('nocmar',	'Hello. I\'m Nocmar.'),
('nocmar_complete',	'By the Shadow. You actually found a heartstone. I thought I wouldn\'t live to see the day.'),
('nocmar_complete_2',	'Can you see the glow? It\'s literally pulsating.'),
('nocmar_complete_3',	'Quick. Let\'s get these old heartsteel weapons glowing again.'),
('nocmar_complete_4',	'*Nocmar places the heartstone among the heartsteel weapons*'),
('nocmar_complete_5',	'Can you feel it? The heartsteel is glowing again.'),
('nocmar_continue',	'Have you found a heartstone yet?'),
('nocmar_continue_2',	'Please keep looking. Unnmir must have something important planned for you.'),
('nocmar_quest',	'Unnmir sent you huh? I guess it must be important then.'),
('nocmar_quest_1',	'Ok, these old weapons have lost their inner glow now that they haven\'t been used in a while.'),
('nocmar_quest_2',	'To make the heartsteel glow again, we will need a heartstone.'),
('nocmar_quest_3',	'Years ago, we used to fight the liches of Undertell. I have no idea if they still haunt the place.'),
('nocmar_quest_4',	'Undertell; the pits of the lost souls. Travel south and enter the caverns of the Dwarves. Follow the horrid smell from there.'),
('nocmar_quest_5',	'Beware the liches of Undertell, if they are still are around. Those things can kill you by their gaze alone.'),
('nocmar_trade_1',	'I don\'t have any items for sale. I used to have a lot of things for sale, but nowadays I\'m not allowed to sell anything.'),
('nocmar_trade_2',	'I was once one of the greatest smiths in Fallhaven. Then that bastard Lord Geomyr banned my use of heartsteel.'),
('nocmar_trade_3',	'By decree of Lord Geomyr, no one in Fallhaven is allowed to even use heartsteel weapons. Much less sell any.'),
('nocmar_trade_4',	'So now I have to hide the few weapons I have left. I won\'t dare sell any of them anymore.'),
('nocmar_trade_4_1',	'I haven\'t seen the heartsteel glow in several years now that Lord Geomyr has banned them.'),
('nocmar_trade_5',	'So, unfortunately I can\'t sell you any of my weapons.'),
('norath_1',	'Hello there. Can I help you?'),
('norath_2',	'Me? No, I don\'t have anything to sell you. Does this look like a shop to you?'),
('norath_3',	'Well, usually I tend to the crops that we grow here. Now, I can\'t find the strength to do that though.'),
