('oluag_1_1',	'Hello. I am Oluag.'),
('oluag_2',	'Oh these. They are nothing. Never mind them. That grave over there is nothing to worry about either.'),
('oluag_boxes_1',	'No no, nothing suspicious at all. It\'s not like they contain any contraband or anything like that, hah!'),
('oluag_goodbye',	'Right. Goodbye.'),
('oluag_grave_1',	'Yeah, ok. So there is a grave right over there. I promise I had nothing to do with it.'),
('oluag_grave_10',	'And he told me something about that he didn\'t dare tell anyone.'),
('oluag_grave_11',	'Yeah sure, probably. He had set down here to camp, but got attacked by some monsters.'),
('oluag_grave_12',	'Apparently he was not as strong a fighter as, for example, someone like me. So the monsters wounded him too much for him to last the night.'),
('oluag_grave_13',	'Sadly, they also must have taken any loot with them, since I could not find any on him.'),
('oluag_grave_14',	'I heard the fighting and only managed to get to him after the monsters had fled.'),
('oluag_grave_15',	'So, anyway. Now he is buried over there. Rest in peace.'),
('oluag_grave_16',	'Lousy kid. He could at least have had a few coins on him.'),
('oluag_grave_2',	'Well, when I say \'nothing\', I really mean nothing. Or maybe just a little bit.'),
('oluag_grave_3',	'Ok, so maybe I just had a little bit to do with it.'),
('oluag_grave_4',	'Relax, relax. I don\'t want any more fights.'),
('oluag_grave_5',	'There was this kid I found. He had almost bled to death.'),
('oluag_grave_6',	'I managed to get a few sentences out of him before he died.'),
('oluag_grave_7',	'So I buried him over there by that grave.'),
('oluag_grave_8',	'Something about Vilegard and Ryndel maybe? I didn\'t really pay attention, I was more interested in what loot he had on him.'),
('oluag_grave_9',	'Yeah, that might be it. Anyway, so he said something about fulfilling a dream to see the great city of Feygard.'),
('oluag_grave_return',	'Look, I already told you the story.'),
