('remgardb_1',	'Halt! No one is allowed to enter or exit Remgard.'),
('remgardb_2',	'Wrong? You bet there is. Several of the townspeople have disappeared, and we are still conducting the investigation.'),
('remgardb_3',	'We are searching for them in the town, and questioning everyone for clues on where they might be.'),
('remgardb_4',	'No, I highly doubt that.'),
('remgardb_5',	'Considering our town is surrounded by lake Laeroth, we guards are able to keep a watchful eye on everything going on here. We are able to keep a log of who comes and goes, since this bridge is our only connection to the mainland.'),
('remgardb_6',	'For your sake, it is probably safer for you to remain out of town until our investigation is complete.'),
('remgardb_7',	'No. As I said, no one except us guards are allowed to enter or exit town until our investigation is completed. I suggest you leave now.'),
