('remgardb_help_10',	'Excellent. Report back as soon as possible.'),
('remgardb_help_2',	'Tell you what. You might be able to help us.'),
('remgardb_help_2b',	'There is an abandoned house some way to the east of here, on a peninsula on the northern shore of lake Laeroth.'),
('remgardb_help_3',	'We have reason to believe that this cabin is inhabited by someone, since we have seen candlelight coming from there during the night across the lake. We are not certain though, it could just be the moonlight on the water.'),
('remgardb_help_4',	'That\'s where you come in, and might be able to help us.'),
