('remgardb_help_return',	'Did you find anything in that abandoned house?'),
('remgardb_helped_1',	'You should go visit our village elder, Jhaeld, and talk to him about what we should do next. I will let you enter Remgard to speak to him.'),
('remgardb_helped_2',	'You can probably find him in the tavern to the southeast, since that\'s where he spends most of his time.'),
('remgardb_helped_n',	'Thank you for scouting that cabin. It\'s a relief to hear that it is empty. Our fears might not be true then after all.'),
