('rogorn_completed_1',	'Thank you for listening to our side of the story.'),
('rogorn_first_1',	'Look fellas, a kid! Out strolling here in the wilderness!'),
('rogorn_first_2',	'Should you really be out here kid? These areas are dangerous.'),
('rogorn_first_3',	'I bet you can.'),
('rogorn_first_4',	'Well, west of here is not much. No towns for quite a while, only the harsh and dangerous wilderness.'),
('rogorn_first_5',	'Of course, there is Carn Tower if you travel really far west, but you really do not want to head there.'),
('rogorn_first_6',	'So, what brings you to these parts of the land?'),
('rogorn_first_7',	'Well, keep on looking then.'),
('rogorn_henchman_1',	'Should you really be out here all by yourself?'),
('rogorn_henchman_atk',	'For the Shadow!'),
('rogorn_henchman_noatk',	'Good to hear that there are at least a few people left out there willing to take a stand against Feygard.'),
('rogorn_story_1',	'That depends, why do you want to know?'),
('rogorn_story_10',	'Law and order? What use do we have of that if we are always persecuted by them and do not even have the freedom to live our lives the way we want?'),
('rogorn_story_11',	'They are always looking for us, trying to oppress us in some way. Always trying to make our lives a little bit harder.'),
('rogorn_story_12',	'Good to hear that there still are some people willing to make a stand against Feygard. Let me tell you my side of the story.'),
('rogorn_story_2',	'Hah! We? Crimes?'),
('rogorn_story_3',	'Justice? What would you know of justice, kid?'),
('rogorn_story_4',	'If there is someone that deserves punishment, it surely isn\'t us. By the Shadow, it\'s those snobs from Feygard that should be taught a lesson.'),
('rogorn_story_5',	'I tell you, we did not steal anything from those snobs.'),
('rogorn_story_6',	'Talked to those guards from Feygard eh? Tell me, what is your opinion of Feygard?'),
('rogorn_story_7',	'Interesting. But now that you are part of their business by coming here to look for me on their behalf, how does that fit into your unwillingness to take sides?'),
('rogorn_story_8',	'You should make up your mind about what your priorities are. Tell your Feygard friends that we will not be oppressed by them. Shadow be with you, child.'),
('rogorn_story_9',	'You have got that right. They are always trying to make life hard for us little people. Let me tell you my side of the story.'),
('rogorn_story_r_1',	'Me and my boys here travelled from our home in Nor City to these northern lands a few days ago.'),
('rogorn_story_r_10',	'You tell those guards that you searched for us, but did not find anyone.'),
('rogorn_story_r_2',	'We had never been here ourselves. We had only heard stories about how tough the guards from Feygard were, and how they held their precious law above all.'),
('rogorn_story_r_3',	'Anyway, we got wind of a certain business opportunity here up north. One where we would be on the receiving end of a very profitable deal.'),
('rogorn_story_r_4',	'So we went here to conduct our business. Shortly thereafter, I guess the guards from Feygard must have been tipped off about us, since we noticed that we were being followed by the guards after a while.'),
('rogorn_story_r_5',	'Not willing to risk anything, considering the rumors we had heard about the guards from there, we did the only reasonable thing we could do - we abandoned the plan right away and left, before we could conduct the business we had planned.'),
('rogorn_story_r_6',	'However, something must have upset the guards there anyway. Now we hear that we are accused of murder and theft in Feygard, without even being there ourselves.'),
('rogorn_story_r_7',	'I can\'t really say. We do our business on behalf of Nor City, and our business is our own.'),
('rogorn_story_r_8',	'What are you, a spy for Feygard? I told you, the accusations against us are false.'),
('rogorn_story_r_9',	'Thank you for listening to our side of the story.'),
('rogorn_toldstory_1',	'You are back.'),
('rolwynn',	'What have we done to deserve this? Please, will you help us?'),
('rolwynn_1',	'My guess is that this must be something done by those arrogant people from Feygard.'),
('rolwynn_2',	'They are always looking for ways to make our lives a little bit harder.'),
('rolwynn_3',	'We try to farm our lands to feed ourselves, but they demand that they get a share of whatever we bring in.'),
('rolwynn_4',	'Lately, the crops haven\'t been as good as they used to be, and the guards apparently think we are withholding some part of their share.'),
('rolwynn_5',	'I am sure that they did something to us as punishment for not following their *rules*. They are always talking about how the laws and rules are so precious to them.'),
('rothses_1',	'Hi. How may I help you? A new set of boots perhaps, or some new gloves?'),
('rothses_19',	'Look, I told you before.'),
('rothses_2',	'It\'s ok, I guess. Not as good as I would like it to be, now that the gates to the town are closed. But people here still seem to need new pieces of leather every now and then.'),
