('sign_snakecave3_grave',	'The ground around the grave is full of small holes, probably by something that has slithered its way to its nest down there. The cross has some writing on it, but you cannot understand what it says.'),
('sign_toszylae_1',	'(Among the remains of the lich \'Toszylae\' that you defeated, you find a strange looking helmet.)'),
('sign_toszylae_2',	'(You see the remains of the lich \'Toszylae\' that you defeated.)'),
('sign_ulirfendor_1',	'In front of the shrine, you find a book laying in the sand. \'Reflections on Kazaul rituals\'.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_10',	'The movements start to get more visible, almost as if there\'s something crawling under the sand.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_11',	'As you get closer to the end of the ritual, the helmet falls forward, face down in the sand.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_12',	'Once you speak the final words of the ritual, the ground sinks slightly in front of the shrine, taking part of the helmet down under the sand.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_13',	'As you pull it out and dust off the sand, you notice a change in texture on the part that was submerged in the sand.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_14',	'You take the helmet, and examine it more closely.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_15',	'Along the side, you notice some ornaments that were not there before. The helmet also gives a slight tingling feeling in the hands as you hold it.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_16',	'Completing the ritual must have restored the helmet to its former glory.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_2',	'You quickly look through the book, and find several chants and rituals of Kazaul.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_3',	'There is one in particular that you spot, that talks of imbuing ancient artifacts with the power of Kazaul.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_4',	'The ritual itself would require the heart of a lich, and from the text surrounding the ritual in the book, it could surely restore the helmet to its former glory.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_5',	'You place yourself in front of the shrine, kneeling like the drawings in the book show.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_6',	'You place the helmet on the ground in front of you, leaning it slightly against the shrine.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_7',	'You place the heart of the lich beside the helmet in front of the shrine.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_8',	'You start reciting the words of the Kazaul tongue from the book, taking great care of saying the words exactly as the book states them.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_9',	'As you speak the words, you notice a faint glow coming from the shrine, and you get the eerie feeling that the sand on the ground almost moves by itself.'),
('sign_ulirfendor_r',	'You see the shrine of Kazaul, where you performed the Kazaul ritual.'),
('sign_vilegard_n',	'The sign says:\nWelcome to Vilegard, the friendliest town around.'),
