('siola',	'Hello there. Have you come to browse my selection of items?'),
('siola_sienn_1',	'I don\'t know where he got it from. Anyway, they don\'t harm anyone, so I\'m fine with them being in here. I figured someone should help them have some place to stay, and no one else wanted to help them, so I let them stay here.'),
('siola_sienn_2',	'Sienn may be a bit thick, but he sure can be funny when you get to know him and he trusts you. He can do a lot of those hilarious facial expressions.'),
('skylenar',	'May you forever walk with the Shadow, my child.'),
('skylenar_1',	'I provide .. guidance to those that seek it. The Shadow guides us. It keeps us safe and comforts us when we sleep.'),
('skylenar_2',	'Lately, it seems Remgard has been in dire need of the comfort that the Shadow provides.'),
('smuggler1_0',	'[mutter] Just one more...'),
('smuggler2_0',	'What? No, you\'re not it.'),
('smuggler3_0',	'[drool]'),
('smuggler3_1',	'[wipes drool]'),
('smuggler3_2',	'[blank stare]'),
('smuggler3_3',	'[makes slurping sounds with drool still left in the corner of the mouth]'),
('smuggler4_0',	'Uhh. Lowyna sure makes the best stuff!'),
('smuggler4_1',	'These of course! [swings his jug, nearly spilling some of it]'),
('smuggler4_2',	'She\'s over there .. no. Over there .. no. Oh, she\'s around here somewhere.'),
('smuggler5_1',	'[blank stare]'),
('smuggler5_2',	'Um. Just one more. Please, just one more.'),
('smuggler6_1',	'Can you spare some gold?'),
('smuggler6_2',	'Oh, oh! I haven\'t seen that much gold in my whole life. I\'m finally rich!'),
('smuggler6_3',	'Is that all you have?'),
('smuggler7_1',	'I\'ve seen them. Their camps.'),
('smuggler7_2',	'The Sakul are watching us. They\'re coming.'),
('snakemaster',	'Well well, what have we here? A visitor, how nice. I\'m impressed you got this far through all my minions.\n\nNow prepare to die, puny creature.'),
('taevinn',	'Please, you must help us!'),
('taevinn_1',	'I\'ll tell you what I know. We try to follow the law around here. Without rules and laws, how would we be any different from the savages that roam the southern lands?'),
('taevinn_2',	'But even if we here in Loneford keep as peaceful as possible, there\'s always someone that has a desire to cause mischief.'),
('taevinn_3',	'Have you seen him? That fool Sienn. Him and his \'pet\' are always trying to cause some trouble. We can\'t have that around here in our friendly village. Especially not in times like these when we are trying to show our good side to those magnificent guards from Feygard that are here.'),
('taevinn_4',	'Did you know I tried to talk to him on several occasions about his so called \'pet\'? I couldn\'t really make out what he was trying to tell me, but that thing of his nearly tried to kill me, it did!'),
('taevinn_5',	'I tell you, there\'s mischief all around him and that thing he keeps around. I am sure they are up to something. They probably caused this illness somehow. Maybe we caught something contagious from that thing of his that he keeps around?'),
('talion_0',	'Shadow be with you.'),
('talion_1',	'The people of Loneford are very keen on following the will of Feygard, whatever it may be.'),
('talion_2',	'Normally, this would not be a problem. But Lord Geomyr seems to have something against the Shadow. He will do almost anything to oppose all actions that in some way extend the reach of the Shadow.'),
('talion_3',	'Because of this, the people of Loneford are now actively abolishing the thought of the Shadow guiding them through their lives.'),
('talion_4',	'People around here would rather follow the law of Feygard than follow the old ways.'),
('talion_5',	'My feeling is that this illness is caused by the Shadow, as punishment to all of us here in Loneford.'),
('talion_bless_1',	'I am able to bless you with either the Shadow\'s strength, regeneration, accuracy, or even the blessing of the Shadow guardian.'),
('talion_bless_2',	'There. I hope you will find it useful on your travels.'),
('talion_bless_acc_1',	'The blessing of Shadow accuracy grants you a keen sense of where best to strike your opponent, thus increasing the chance of a successful hit while fighting. I can give you the blessing for 250 gold.'),
('talion_bless_acc_2',	'Very well. *starts chanting*'),
('talion_bless_guard_1',	'Ah yes, the blessing of the Shadow guardian. The Shadow protects you in dark places, and keeps you safe where others might not see. I can give you the blessing for 400 gold.'),
('talion_bless_guard_2',	'Very well. *starts chanting*'),
('talion_bless_heal_1',	'The blessing of Shadow regeneration will slowly heal you back if you get hurt. I can give you the blessing for 250 gold.'),
('talion_bless_heal_2',	'Very well. *starts chanting*'),
('talion_bless_str_1',	'The blessing of Shadow strength grants you more strength while attacking, thus increasing the amount of damage you do on each hit. I can give you the blessing for 300 gold.'),
('talion_bless_str_2',	'Very well. *starts chanting*'),
('talion_bone_1',	'Oh, good. Please, give them to me.'),
('talion_bone_2',	'Thank you.'),
('talion_cure_1',	'That\'s all I need to cure you. Good work.'),
('talion_cure_2',	'Now, let\'s get this cure started. I just need to grind this .. and mix those .. and ..'),
('talion_cure_3',	'Give me a minute.'),
('talion_cure_4',	'(Talion mixes the ground up ingredients together in the vial you brought, with some leaves and berries that he kept with him.)'),
('talion_cure_5',	'(He gives the potion a thorough shake for quite a while.)'),
('talion_cure_6',	'There. Drink this. This should do it.'),
('talion_cure_7',	'(The potion smells rancid, but you manage to drink it all down. The pain from the stomach decreases, and you feel one of the rotworms crawling up into your mouth. You quickly spit the worm out into the now empty vial.)'),
('talion_cured_1',	'Ah, that seems to have worked. Frankly, I was a little worried that it might not have worked, but seeing you spit out that worm really confirms it. Ha ha.'),
('talion_cured_10',	'Yes. Well .. for a fee of course.'),
('talion_cured_2',	'Yes. Nasty, aren\'t they? *chuckle*'),
('talion_cured_3',	'That one worm you spit out, you should make sure you hold on to that. It might be valuable in the future.'),
('talion_cured_4',	'Well, you never know. Some people really like .. exotic things.'),
('talion_cured_5',	'It\'s your choice of course.'),
('talion_cured_7',	'Now, I know you must have gone through a lot to get infected with these things. You seem like the experienced type.'),
('talion_cured_8',	'Tell you what, I don\'t normally offer this to anyone, but you seem like you could use the help.'),
('talion_cured_9',	'Seeing as you managed to pull through all of this, I would be willing to offer you the help of giving you blessings of the Shadow if you want.'),
('talion_demon_1',	'Just to be sure, you did kill whatever creature that infected you with this, right?'),
('talion_demon_2',	'Good. Then I am able to help you.'),
('talion_demon_3',	'Then you better go take care of that first!'),
('talion_gather_r',	'No need, you already brought me that before. But thank you anyway.'),
('talion_hair_1',	'Oh, good. Please, give them to me.'),
('talion_hair_2',	'Thank you.'),
('talion_infect_1',	'Oh my, what has happened to you? You don\'t look too well.'),
('talion_infect_10',	'No, unfortunately not. Not with this few supplies I\'m sorry.'),
('talion_infect_11',	'For this particular cure to work, I would need help with gathering four items.'),
('talion_infect_12',	'Or .. well .. actually, eight items in total, but four different types. Eh .. well, you get the idea.'),
('talion_infect_13',	'Anyway, what you need to bring me is, first and foremost, some more fresh bones. Five bones will do I think. Make sure they are fresh. Any old skeleton will do, but I\'d rather take some fresh bones of some nasty animal.'),
('talion_infect_14',	'Secondly, I will need some animal fur to go with that. Two pieces of animal hair will surely do. I\'m sure any old animal fur from the wilderness outside town will do.'),
('talion_infect_15',	'Third, I will need a gland of poison from a creature called the Irdegh.'),
('talion_infect_16',	'Now, I have not seen an Irdegh myself, but I hear they are particularly nasty creatures. Venomous like nothing I\'ve heard of.'),
('talion_infect_17',	'Some people have talked about seeing some of them far to the east, across the bridges.'),
('talion_infect_18',	'Lastly, I would need a clean empty vial to make the potion in. I hear that the potion-maker in Fallhaven has the best vials available.'),
('talion_infect_19',	'Bring me these things and I will be able to help you with your .. condition.'),
('talion_infect_2',	'Ah, my old friend Ulirfendor. It\'s good to hear that he is still alive. Wait! What was that? Rotworms you say, eh?'),
('talion_infect_3',	'Nasty things, they are. I have seen people going mad from the stomach pains, and I have seen people being eaten alive from the inside.'),
('talion_infect_30',	'You return. Have you gathered those things that I asked for?'),
('talion_infect_31',	'There are still some more of those items that I need.'),
('talion_infect_4',	'It\'s good that you came to see me. I might be able to help you.'),
('talion_infect_5',	'A lich of Kazaul eh? Then I am sure that whatever ails you are those cursed rotworms.'),
('talion_infect_6',	'However, there is a slight problem. You see, normally my supply of potions and ingredients would be fully stocked. However with this trouble that we have here in Loneford, my supplies are lower than they have ever been before.'),
('talion_infect_7',	'I am not even able to go out and gather new supplies, what with the illness and all.'),
('talion_infect_8',	'You know what, maybe you can go out and gather some items for me. With your condition, it is important that we hurry as much as we can.'),
('talion_infect_9',	'Yes, I guess I should have.'),
('talion_irdegh_1',	'Oh, good. Please, give it to me.'),
('talion_irdegh_2',	'Thank you.'),
('talion_vial_1',	'Oh, good. Please, give it to me.'),
('talion_vial_2',	'Thank you.'),
('taylin',	'No, get away! They can\'t find me here. Don\'t give away my good hiding spot!'),
('telund',	'Who are you? Have you seen my father Selgan? They all tell me he will be back shortly, but they are all lying! I know it, I know it! He wasn\'t home yesterday, and he isn\'t home today.'),
('tharal1',	'Walk in the glow of the Shadow, my child.'),
('tharal_antifoodp1',	'No, sorry. I hear that the potion-maker in Fallhaven can create something to help against that though.'),
('tharal_antifoodp2',	'You should go see him and ask if he has anything to help against that. He can probably help you.'),
('tharal_bonemeal1',	'Bonemeal? We shouldn\'t talk about that. Lord Geomyr issued a decree. It\'s not allowed anymore.'),
('tharal_bonemeal2',	'Well if you really are that persistent. Bring me 5 insect wings that I can use for making potions and maybe we can talk more.'),
('tharal_bonemeal2_1',	'No, we really shouldn\'t talk about that.'),
('tharal_bonemeal3',	'Thanks kid. I knew I could count on you.'),
('tharal_bonemeal4',	'Oh yes, bonemeal. Mixed with the right components it can be one of the most effective healing agents around.'),
('tharal_bonemeal5',	'We used to use it extensively before. But now that bastard Lord Geomyr has banned all use of it.'),
('tharal_bonemeal6',	'How am I supposed to heal people now? Using regular healing potions? Bah, they\'re so ineffective.'),
('tharal_bonemeal7',	'I know someone that still has a supply of Bonemeal if you are interested. Go talk to Thoronir, a fellow priest in Fallhaven. Tell him my password \'Glow of the Shadow\'.'),
('tharwyn_1',	'Hello there. I heard you helped Jolnor in the chapel. You have my thanks, friend.'),
('tharwyn_2',	'Have a seat anywhere. What can I get you?'),
('thievesguild_cook_1',	'Hello, did you want something?'),
('thievesguild_cook_10',	'Yes, I gave you the special brew earlier.'),
('thievesguild_cook_2',	'That\'s right. Someone has to keep these ruffians fed.'),
('thievesguild_cook_3',	'Thanks. This stew is coming along nicely.'),
('thievesguild_cook_4',	'Yeah, I know. With ingredients this bad, what can you do? Anyway, it keeps us fed.'),
('thievesguild_cook_5',	'Oh sure. Planning to get someone a bit sleepy eh?'),
('thievesguild_cook_6',	'Don\'t worry, I won\'t tell anyone. Making sleepy food is one of my specialties.'),
('thievesguild_cook_7',	'Give me a minute to mix it up for you.'),
('thievesguild_cook_8',	'There. This should do it. Here you go.'),
('thievesguild_cook_9',	'Be careful not to get any of that stuff on your fingers, it is really potent.'),
('thievesguild_pickpocket_1',	'Hello there.'),
('thievesguild_pickpocket_2',	'My real name is unimportant. People mostly call me Quickfingers.'),
('thievesguild_pickpocket_3',	'Well, I have a tendency to .. how shall I put this .. acquire certain things easily.'),
('thievesguild_pickpocket_4',	'Things previously in the possession of other people.'),
('thievesguild_pickpocket_5',	'No no. I wouldn\'t call it stealing. It\'s more of a transfer of ownership. To me, that is.'),
('thievesguild_pickpocket_6',	'After all, we are the Thieves\' Guild. What did you expect?'),
('thievesguild_thief_1',	'Hello kid.'),
('thievesguild_thief_2',	'This is our guild hall. We are safe from the guards of Fallhaven in here.'),
('thievesguild_thief_3',	'We can do pretty much as we like here. As long as Umar allows it, that is.'),
('thievesguild_thief_4',	'He is probably in his room over there. *points*'),
('thievesguild_thief_5',	'Umar is our guild leader. He decides our rules and guides us in moral decisions.'),
('thievesguild_troublemaker_1',	'Hello. Don\'t I recognize you from somewhere?'),
('thievesguild_troublemaker_2',	'I keep an eye on our supplies for the guild.'),
('thievesguild_troublemaker_3',	'No, I really recognize you.'),
('thievesguild_troublemaker_4',	'Yes, might be.'),
('thievesguild_troublemaker_5',	'Oh yes, now that you mention it. There was that kid running around here, asking a lot of questions.'),
('thievesguild_troublemaker_6',	'No. I don\'t know. I just manage the supplies.'),
('thorin_1',	'What\'s this, a visitor? How unexpected.'),
('thorin_2',	'Tell me, what can Thorin do for you?'),
('thorin_decline',	'Too bad. Good day to you then.'),
('thorin_rest_n',	'My bed? No, that\'s mine. Maybe I will let you use it if you help me with a small task.'),
('thorin_rest_y',	'Please, go ahead. You may rest here as much as you like.'),
('thorin_return_1',	'My friend returns. What can Thorin do for you?'),
('thorin_search_1',	'Welcome back. Did you find all six of them?'),
('thorin_search_2',	'Ok then. Please return when you have found them all. I would go search myself if those nasty bugs weren\'t there.'),
('thorin_search_c_1',	'Thank you. I would have gone myself if those nasty bugs weren\'t there. This turned out to be much easier though.'),
('thorin_search_c_2',	'As a token of my appreciation, you are welcome to use the bed over there to rest. Also, if you are interested in healing, I might be able to provide some help.'),
('thorin_story_1',	'You see, me and my fellow gatherers were out investigating the poisonous nature of the Irdegh.'),
('thorin_story_10',	'If you could find me their remains, I would be most grateful. Maybe I could continue my investigation based on their remains. Hmm, yes that would be great.'),
('thorin_story_11',	'Excellent. Bring me back the remains of all six of them. I would go search myself if those nasty bugs weren\'t there.'),
('thorin_story_2',	'Apparently, I was the only one that was careful enough when handling our wares.'),
('thorin_story_3',	'The others got ill quite quick, and we hid in this cave to rest up. However, we had not anticipated these bugs in here.'),
('thorin_story_4',	'Those \'Scaradon\' things are tough! They did not even seem to take any damage when I hit them.'),
('thorin_story_5',	'So, that\'s where I am now. The people that sent us to investigate told us to set up camp if we encountered any problems, and they would come help us.'),
('thorin_story_6',	'So far, you are the first visitor here for quite a while.'),
('thorin_story_6_1',	'Nah, it\'s just business. Just business.'),
('thorin_story_7',	'Hmm. Yes, actually there is something that you could do for me.'),
('thorin_story_8',	'The others that I was travelling with, they did not make it this far into the cave, but got attacked by those bugs closer to the entrance.'),
('thorin_story_9',	'Considering how they died, I would be very interested in seeing what effects both the Irdegh and the Scaradons had on them.'),
('thorin_trade_n',	'No. I might have something to trade if you help me with a small task.'),
('thorin_trade_y',	'Oh yes. The upside of this cave is that it literally is crawling with dead bodies of those Scaradon bugs.'),
('thorin_trade_y2',	'By chance, I happened to find out that with the right mixture, they can be made into a healing substance.'),
('thorin_what_1',	'Oh, not much. Well actually, I am waiting for someone - or rather, some people.'),
('thorin_who_1',	'Oh, I did not introduce me, my apologies. I am Thorin.'),
('thoronir_church_1',	'This is our chapel of worship in Fallhaven. Our community turns to us for support.'),
('thoronir_church_2',	'This church has withstood hundreds of years, and has been kept safe from grave robbers.'),
('thoronir_church_3',	'The catacombs beneath the church house the remains of our passed leaders. Our great King Luthor is rumored to be buried there.'),
('thoronir_church_4',	'No one is allowed down in the catacombs, except for Athamyr, my apprentice. He is the only one that has been down there for years.'),
('thoronir_complete_2',	'Give me some time to mix the Bonemeal potion. It is a very potent healing potion. Come back in a little while.'),
('thoronir_default',	'Bask in the Shadow, my child.'),
('thoronir_shadow_1',	'The Shadow protects us from the dangers of the night. It keeps us safe and comforts us when we sleep.'),
('thoronir_tharal_1',	'Glow of the Shadow indeed my child. So my old friend Tharal in Crossglen village sent you?'),
('thoronir_tharal_2',	'Shhh, we shouldn\'t talk so loud about using Bonemeal. As you know, Lord Geomyr issued a ban on all use of Bonemeal.'),
('thoronir_tharal_3',	'When the ban came, I did not dare keep any, so I threw my whole supply away. It was quite foolish now that I look back on it.'),
('thoronir_tharal_4',	'Do you think you could find me 5 skeletal bones that I can use for mixing a Bonemeal potion? The bonemeal is very potent in healing old wounds.'),
('thoronir_tharal_5',	'Thank you, please come back soon. I heard there were some undead near an old abandoned house just north of Fallhaven. Maybe you can check for bones there?'),
('thoronir_tharal_complete',	'Thank you, these bones will do fine. Now I can start creating some bonemeal healing potions for you.'),
('thoronir_trade_bonemeal',	'Yes, the Bonemeal potions are ready. Please use them with care, and don\'t let the guards see you. We are not actually allowed to use them anymore.'),
('throdna_1',	'Kazaul.. Shadow.. what was it again?'),
('throdna_10',	'The ritual. We believe that Kazaul will manifest in our presence soon.'),
('throdna_11',	'We must learn more about the Kazaul ritual, to gain its power and learn to use it for our purposes.'),
('throdna_12',	'As I said, we want to learn more about the ritual itself.'),
('throdna_13',	'A while ago, we were on the verge of getting our hands on the whole ritual itself, but the messenger was killed under most interesting circumstances while traveling up here.'),
('throdna_14',	'We knew he had the parts of the complete ritual on him, but since he was killed and we could not get to him because of the monsters - his notes were lost to us.'),
('throdna_15',	'According to our sources, there should be five parts of the ritual scattered across the mountain. Three of them describing the ritual itself, and two describing the Kazaul chant used to summon the guardian.'),
('throdna_16',	'Hm, maybe you could be of use here..'),
('throdna_17',	'Fine, we will just have to find someone else then.'),
('throdna_18',	'Yes, you might be able to help. Not that you really have any choice though.'),
('throdna_19',	'Ok. Find me the pieces of the ritual that the former messenger carried on him. They should be found somewhere on the path up to Blackwater Mountain.'),
('throdna_2',	'Oh, a visitor. Hello there. I have not seen you around here before. Did they let you in here?'),
('throdna_20',	'Yes, you will.'),
('throdna_3',	'Of course they did. What am I rambling on about. Harlenn and his gang always keep their worldly duties under control.'),
('throdna_4',	'So, who might you be then, eh? Probably here to bother me with some worldly complaint about the settlement needing more resources or someone complaining about the cold drag from the outside again?'),
('throdna_5',	'And there you go with your mundane problems. I tell you, your worldly troubles do not interest me the least bit.'),
('throdna_6',	'This is the mages\' chamber in Blackwater Mountain. We devote our time to the studies of the Shadow and its descendants.'),
('throdna_7',	'I am Throdna. One of the most learned persons around, if you ask me.'),
('throdna_8',	'Kazaul, the Shadow spawn of red marrow.'),
('throdna_9',	'We have been trying to read all we can on Kazaul, and the ritual. It seems we might be too late.'),
('throdna_check_fail',	'It seems you have not found all five pieces yet.'),
('throdna_guard',	'Keep your voice down while in the inner chamber.'),
('throdna_loop_1',	'What do you want?'),
('throdna_purify_1',	'Hello again. I hope you are here to tell me you have purified the shrine of Kazaul?'),
('throdna_purify_2',	'Then hurry and go take the vial to the shrine! What are you standing around here for?'),
('throdna_purify_3',	'Good. We must hurry to continue our research on Kazaul.'),
('throdna_purify_4',	'You should get out of here to allow us to concentrate on our work.'),
('throdna_purify_5',	'.. Kazaul, destroyer of bright dreams ..'),
('throdna_purify_6',	'.. Kazaul .. Shadow ..'),
('throdna_purify_7',	'(Throdna continues to mumble on about Kazaul, but you cannot make out any other words)'),
('throdna_return_1',	'Hello again. I hope you come here to tell me you have the five parts of the ritual.'),
('throdna_return_10',	'Second, we need you to take a vial of purifying spirit and apply it to the shrine.'),
('throdna_return_11',	'This vial is a vial of purifying spirit. It should delay the process well enough for us to be able to continue our research.'),
('throdna_return_12',	'Good, here is the vial. Now hurry.'),
('throdna_return_13',	'Return to me as soon as you have completed your task.'),
('throdna_return_2',	'Then hurry and go find them! What are you standing around here for then?'),
('throdna_return_3',	'You actually found all five pieces? I suppose I should thank you. Well then. Thank you.'),
('throdna_return_4',	'We have more pressing matters to focus on. As I briefly mentioned before, we believe that Kazaul will manifest in our presence soon.'),
('throdna_return_5',	'If that were to happen, we could not complete our research about the ritual or Kazaul itself, all our efforts would be lost.'),
('throdna_return_6',	'Therefore, we intend to delay the process as much as we can, until we have learned of its powers.'),
('throdna_return_7',	'You might be useful to us here again.'),
('throdna_return_8',	'We need you to do two things. First, you must find the shrine of Kazaul. Our scouts tell us that the shrine should be located somewhere near the base of Blackwater Mountain.'),
('throdna_return_9',	'However, all passageways to the shrine are \'clouded in Shadow\' according to our scouts. I\'m not sure what that means.'),
('thukuzun',	'Ah, another mortal that has come to bow before the might of Thukuzun.'),
('thukuzun_1',	'You will be a fine specimen in my army of bones.'),
('tinlyn_benbyr_1',	'Is he still around? I thought the guards got the best of him.'),
('tinlyn_benbyr_2',	'Anyway, I do not want to talk about that. I have left that kind of life behind me. Herding sheep is what I do now.'),
('tinlyn_complete_1',	'Hello again. Thank you for helping me find my lost sheep.'),
('tinlyn_decline_1',	'Oh well, it didn\'t hurt to ask.'),
('tinlyn_found_1',	'Yes, I can hear distant sounds of bells from the fields to the south. I am sure they will come back here now that they have the bells on them.'),
('tinlyn_found_2',	'I am sorry, but I am a simple shepherd. I have no wealth or magical trinkets to give you.'),
('tinlyn_found_3',	'Thank you for helping me.'),
('tinlyn_killedsheep_1',	'You attacked my sheep! Get away from me you filthy murderer!'),
('tinlyn_look_1',	'Hello again. Did you find all four of my missing sheep?'),
('tinlyn_lostsheep1_n',	'Baah!'),
