('ulirfendor_1',	'No! Stay away! You shall not defeat me!'),
('ulirfendor_10',	'I have placed a blessing of the Shadow upon this small island here, so that I may work uninterrupted. Strangely enough, it seems to be very effective on them.'),
('ulirfendor_11',	'They seem to be very cautious about it. So far, not even one has dared to approach me. Even those pesky lizards are keeping their distance.'),
('ulirfendor_12',	'It speaks of Kazaul and of the misery that comes to anyone that opposes the will of Kazaul.'),
('ulirfendor_13',	'Something about \'re-birth from within the followers\'. Not sure I have translated that part correctly, but I think that is what it says. Definitely something about re-birth or birth.'),
('ulirfendor_14',	'It also speaks of someone or some .. thing called the \'Dark protector\'. Most parts of the text for that is missing from the shrine however.'),
('ulirfendor_15',	'Whatever it means, it seems important. It is also obvious that the \'Dark protector\' brings power to Kazaul, and misery to any opposition.'),
('ulirfendor_16',	'Regardless, it must be stopped, whatever it means. Maybe it refers to something deeper down this cave? I have not ventured further into the cave to the east since I could not get past those .. things.'),
('ulirfendor_17',	'Forgive me, I must continue translating the few readable parts left on this shrine.'),
('ulirfendor_18',	'Hm, maybe. I need to figure out what this last part should be. Hmm..'),
('ulirfendor_19',	'The last part of this piece has been eroded from the rock. It begins with \'Kulauil hamar urum Kazaul\'te\'. But what is the rest of that?'),
('ulirfendor_19_2',	'Argh, if this cave wasn\'t so damp, I bet the rest of the text would still be there.'),
('ulirfendor_2',	'Oh wait, you are not one of them. You.. you are not one of those spawns.'),
('ulirfendor_20',	'Sure, you do that.'),
('ulirfendor_21',	'I have looked thoroughly for any clues in the western part of this cave, but have not found any. I have not entered the eastern parts of the cave however.'),
('ulirfendor_22',	'Also, I should warn you that I believe the shrine talks of a powerful creature somewhere in this cave. Maybe if you find that creature, it will provide some clue as to what the missing parts are? You need to be careful though.'),
('ulirfendor_4',	'Oh, how long have I been down here? I can\'t remember.'),
('ulirfendor_5',	'No matter. I must finish my work here. You see this shrine here?'),
('ulirfendor_5_1',	'If my understanding is correct, this shrine is a remnant of Kazaul.'),
('ulirfendor_6',	'The writings on it have almost vanished, but I have managed to read parts of it. It speaks in an ancient Kazaul tongue, so all parts are not clear to me.'),
('ulirfendor_7',	'I am sure that this shrine is part of the cause for these .. these .. things .. that lurk in this cave. I will do anything in my power to defeat whatever mischief that comes from it.'),
('ulirfendor_8',	'Ah, the Allaceph. I had not seen one for many years until I entered this cave. They are a remnant of the guardians of Kazaul.'),
('ulirfendor_9',	'Have you noticed how they seem to feed upon whoever tries to fight them? Cursed things, almost got a hold of me, they did.'),
('ulirfendor_bye',	'Thank you. Goodbye.'),
('ulirfendor_cured_1',	'I am glad to see that you are looking better than before. I assume you got the help you needed from Talion in Loneford?'),
('ulirfendor_cured_2',	'That\'s good to hear. I hope that .. thing .. didn\'t have any permanent side-effects on you.'),
('ulirfendor_decline',	'No matter, I will find out myself then. Thank you for your help so far. Goodbye.'),
('ulirfendor_demon_1',	'Yes, you told me that you killed the lich. Excellent work.'),
('ulirfendor_demon_2',	'The people of the surrounding towns will have you to thank.'),
('ulirfendor_demon_d1',	'Oh, that is good news indeed. A lich you say? With your help, the people of the surrounding towns should be safe from whatever mischief the lich could have caused now.'),
('ulirfendor_demon_d2',	'Thank you so much for your help!'),
('ulirfendor_dp_bless_1',	'You truly have a large heart.'),
('ulirfendor_dp_bless_2',	'The blessing will grant you the aid of the Shadow while in combat, protecting you from harmful effects that you opponent might inflict upon you.'),
('ulirfendor_dp_bless_3',	'Very well, I will give you the dark blessing of the Shadow.'),
('ulirfendor_dp_bless_4',	'(Ulirfendor starts chanting in a tongue that you do not recognize.)'),
('ulirfendor_dp_bless_5',	'There. You now have the dark blessing of the Shadow upon you.'),
('ulirfendor_dp_bless_6',	'Thank you yet again for all you have done here.'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_10',	'Now, watch this. I love this part.'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_11',	'(Ulirfendor takes aim with his foot and stomps the helmet with the heel of his boot in a powerful motion.'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_12',	'(The helmet completely shatters, leaving nothing but a fine dust.)'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_13',	'Ha ha! Look at that!'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_14',	'(He does the same with the heart that also seems to have completely frozen and gotten covered with cracks.)'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_15',	'Ah, that sure felt good.'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_16',	'You, my friend, have done a great deed here today. This thing would have brought great misery if it would have fallen into the wrong hands.'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_17',	'The people of the surrounding towns are now safe from whatever misery that helmet would have brought. All thanks to you!'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_18',	'As a token of my appreciation, I am willing to grant upon you a blessing of the Shadow.'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_2',	'Excellent. I will begin the procedure immediately.'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_3',	'(Ulirfendor places the helmet and the lich\'s heart on the ground before him, and opens his backpack of items.)'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_4',	'(He pulls out a leathery potion case from his backpack, and takes out a vial of clear but almost shining liquid.)'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_5',	'(Ulirfendor pours the contents of the vial on the helmet and the heart in circling motions, taking good care to not spill any on the ground.)'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_6',	'It should be as simple as that really. Powerful stuff this.'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_7',	'(The surface of the helmet seems to freeze, almost like it had a layer of ice on it.)'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_8',	'(After a while, small cracks appear on the surface, making tiny sounds as they appear.)'),
('ulirfendor_dp_proc_9',	'(The cracks start to get larger and more dense along the surface, until the helmet is completely covered by them.)'),
('ulirfendor_dp_return1',	'Hello again. Have you made up your mind about what we talked about before?'),
('ulirfendor_findparts_1',	'Hello again. Did you find any clues about what the missing parts are?'),
('ulirfendor_findparts_10',	'Hello again. Did you speak those words to the creature you encountered?'),
('ulirfendor_findparts_11',	'Sure. It\'s \'Klatam ur turum Kazaul\'te\'.'),
('ulirfendor_findparts_12',	'So, did anything happen?'),
('ulirfendor_findparts_13',	'Well, you should probably investigate that area some more. I am sure there are more clues in there about what this shrine speaks of.'),
('ulirfendor_findparts_2',	'If you really want to help, then please go look for any other clues you might find.'),
('ulirfendor_findparts_3',	'Oh good, tell me, did you find any more clues?'),
('ulirfendor_findparts_4',	'Hmm.. \'hamat urul\'.. Yes of course! That\'s what it says on the eroded parts of the shrine!'),
('ulirfendor_findparts_5',	'Excellent work my friend! Now I just need to translate it.'),
('ulirfendor_findparts_6',	'I wonder what this whole piece means. \'Kulauil hamar urum Kazaul\'te. Kazaul hamat urul\' - that\'s the part you heard the creature speak.'),
('ulirfendor_findparts_7',	'The next part is \'Klatam ur turum Kazaul\'te\', and I am not sure what that means. Something about handing over some item?'),
('ulirfendor_findparts_8',	'Maybe the creature you encountered responds to that phrase if you speak to it? If you want to help, you could go and try speaking that phrase to it.'),
('ulirfendor_findparts_9',	'Good. Please return as soon as possible.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_1',	'Could it be? Hmm. Let me look at that thing.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_2',	'Those markings on it are most peculiar. It was found by the lich that you spoke of?'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_3',	'Hmm. You know what, this could actually be connected to what the shrine speaks of - The Dark Protector'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_4',	'I am not certain of what the term \'The Dark Protector\' refers to. At first I thought it might be some creature protecting something, but this helmet seems to fit better in on what the shrine speaks of.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_5',	'It could either be the helmet itself, or that the helmet has some effect on whoever wears it, meaning that the wearer will become the Dark Protector.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_6',	'Nevertheless, I am almost certain that this artifact is connected to what this shrine speaks of, and that the artifact is rich with Kazaul influence.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_7',	'As such, it would most certainly bring misery to the surroundings of whoever carries it. Directly or indirectly, I do not know.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_8',	'I say, we must destroy that item immediately to make sure that the Kazaul taint is forever cleansed from this place and to make sure it does not fall into the wrong hands.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_d1',	'That is most interesting, but you seem to have more pressing matters to attend to.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_keep1',	'What!? Keep it!? Have you gone mad? We need to destroy it to protect the people!'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_keep2',	'What is this!? I knew there was something wrong about you the first time I saw you.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_keep3',	'By the Shadow, I will stop you. Whatever it takes. You will not live to see the next day!'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_n1',	'I\'m glad to hear that.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_n2',	'To destroy it, I think it will suffice to use what we normally use when removing the taint of Kazaul - a vial of purifying spirit.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_n3',	'Fortunately, I always carry some on me, so that won\'t be a problem.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_n4',	'What could be a problem however, is the other thing we will need. This artifact is most likely connected to that lich you encountered.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_n5',	'We would need to use the vial of purifying spirit on something powerful from that lich as well.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_n6',	'The heart? Oh yes, that would surely do.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_n7',	'Quickly now, give me the helmet and the heart of the lich, and I will begin the procedure.'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_n8',	'Think all you want, but please hurry. We need to destroy this thing as soon as possible!'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_power',	'I don\'t even want to think about that. It would surely bring misery to the surroundings of whoever wears it. We must destroy it immediately!'),
('ulirfendor_helmet_worth',	'Worth!? What difference would that make? We need to destroy it immediately!'),
('ulirfendor_infected_1',	'(Ulirfendor gives you a terrified look)'),
('ulirfendor_infected_10',	'No.. can it be? Are they actually real?'),
('ulirfendor_infected_11',	'You show all the signs. If this is true, then you are in great danger.'),
('ulirfendor_infected_12',	'Long ago, I read a book on Kazaul rituals. The first part of one particular ritual I read about talks about \'the carrier\', that supposedly is infected with Kazaul rotworms.'),
('ulirfendor_infected_13',	'The Kazaul rotworms need a living being to feed upon, before their eggs can hatch. Their eggs can slowly kill a person from the inside, and the worms themselves cause the carrier to become weak during the whole process.'),
('ulirfendor_infected_14',	'The ritual proceeds with the carrier being eaten alive by the rotworms and their eggs. Also, the process can have .. shall we say .. unusual effects on the carrier.'),
('ulirfendor_infected_15',	'Needless to say, you are in great danger, and you should seek help immediately.'),
('ulirfendor_infected_16',	'The ritual proceeds with the carrier being eaten from the inside by the rotworms and their eggs, in effect, giving birth to the creatures within. Also, the process can have .. shall we say .. unusual effects on the carrier before that.'),
('ulirfendor_infected_17',	'You should hurry and seek help from one of the priests of the Shadow as quickly as possible. My dear friend Talion in the temple of Loneford should be able to help you.'),
('ulirfendor_infected_18',	'Seek him out immediately. Hurry! You might not have much time.'),
('ulirfendor_infected_19',	'I should also tell you that it is of great importance that you first destroy whatever creature that infected you with this.'),
('ulirfendor_infected_2',	'You are back! Please tell me you are well! Please tell me nothing happened to you!'),
('ulirfendor_infected_3',	'I managed to translate the piece that we spoke about. Oh, what have I done. Please, tell me you are well!'),
('ulirfendor_infected_4',	'Nooo! What have I done?'),
('ulirfendor_infected_5',	'You see, while you were away, I managed to translate the words that we spoke about before.'),
('ulirfendor_infected_6',	'The part that the creature spoke basically means \'No offering is worthy for Kazaul\'.'),
('ulirfendor_infected_7',	'Furthermore, the last part, that I made you speak to the creature, \'Klatam ur turum Kazaul\'te\', means \'My body for Kazaul\'.'),
('ulirfendor_infected_8',	'Oh, what have I done? I made you say it, and now you are touched by its vile essence.'),
('ulirfendor_infected_9',	'Let me have a look at you.'),
('umar_2',	'Last time we talked, you asked for the way to Lodar\'s Hideaway. Did you find it?'),
('umar_3',	'Oh. I must have you mixed up with someone else.'),
('umar_4',	'Really? Never mind I said anything then.'),
('umar_5',	'He came here a while ago, asking a lot of questions about what relation the Thieves\' Guild has to the Shadow and to the royal guard in Feygard.'),
('umar_6',	'We in the Thieves\' Guild really don\'t care much for the Shadow. Nor do we care for the royal guard.'),
('umar_7',	'We try to be above their bickering and differences. They may fight as much as they want, but the Thieves\' Guild will outlive them all.'),
('umar_andor_1',	'He asked me for my support, and asked of how to find Lodar.'),
('umar_andor_2',	'Lodar? He is one of the famous potion makers from the old days. The Thieves\' Guild has requested his services many times before. He can make all sorts of strong sleeping potions, healing potions and cures.'),
('umar_andor_3',	'But his specialty is, of course, his poisons. His poison can harm even the largest of monsters.'),
('umar_andor_4',	'I don\'t know. Maybe he was looking for a potion.'),
('umar_conflict_1',	'Where have you been the last couple of years? Don\'t you know of the brewing conflict?'),
('umar_conflict_2',	'The royal guard, led by Lord Geomyr in Feygard, are trying to ward off the recent increase in illegal activities, and are therefore imposing more restrictions on what is allowed and not.'),
('umar_conflict_3',	'The priests of the Shadow, mostly seated in Nor City, are opponents to the new restrictions, saying that they limit the ways that they can please the Shadow.'),
('umar_conflict_4',	'In turn, the rumor is that the priests of the Shadow are planning to overthrow Lord Geomyr and his forces.'),
('umar_conflict_5',	'Also, the rumor is that the priests of the Shadow are still doing their rituals, despite the fact that most of the rituals have been banned.'),
('umar_conflict_6',	'Lord Geomyr and his royal guard on the other hand, are still trying their best to rule in a way that they feel is fair.'),
('umar_conflict_7',	'We in the Thieves\' Guild try not to get involved in the conflict. Our business is so far unaffected by all of this.'),
('umar_lodar_1',	'I really shouldn\'t tell you. How to get to him is one of our closely guarded secrets in the guild. His hideaway is only reachable by our members.'),
('umar_lodar_2',	'However, I heard that you helped us find the key of Luthor. This is something we have been trying to get to for a long time.'),
('umar_lodar_3',	'Ok, I\'ll tell you how to get to Lodar\'s Hideaway. But you have to promise to keep it a secret. Do not tell anyone. Not even those that appear to be members of the Thieves\' Guild.'),
('umar_lodar_4',	'Good. The thing is, you not only need to find the place itself, but you also need to utter the correct words to be allowed entry by the guardian.'),
('umar_lodar_5',	'The only one that understands the language of the guardian is the old man Ogam in Vilegard.'),
('umar_lodar_6',	'You should travel to the town of Vilegard and find Ogam. He can help you get the right words to enter Lodar\'s Hideaway.'),
('umar_novisit_1',	'Hello. How did your search go?'),
('umar_return_1',	'Hello again, my friend.'),
('umar_return_2',	'Anything else I can help you with?'),
('umar_vilegard_1',	'You travel southeast from Fallhaven. When you reach the main road and the Foaming Flask tavern, head south. It\'s not very far to the southeast from here.'),
('ungorm',	'... but while the forces were withdrawing, the larger part of ...'),
('ungorm_1',	'Oh. A young one. Hello. Please do not disturb my students while they are studying.'),
('unnmir_0',	'Hi there.'),
('unnmir_1',	'That old drunk over at the tavern told you his story did he?'),
('unnmir_10',	'Hey, by the way, are you looking to be an adventurer?'),
('unnmir_11',	'Nice. I\'ll give you a hint, kid. *snickering*. Go see Nocmar over by the west side of town. Tell him I sent you.'),
('unnmir_12',	'Smart move. Adventuring leads to a lot of scars. If you know what I mean.'),
('unnmir_13',	'His house is just southwest of the tavern.'),
('unnmir_2',	'Same old story. We used to travel together a few years back.'),
('unnmir_3',	'Real adventuring you know, swords and spells.'),
('unnmir_4',	'Then, after a while, we stopped. I can\'t really say why, I guess we got tired of life on the road. We settled down here in Fallhaven.'),
('unnmir_5',	'Nice little town here. A lot of thieves around, but they don\'t bother me.'),
('unnmir_6',	'So what\'s your story, kid? How did you end up here in Fallhaven?'),
('unnmir_7',	'Yeah yeah, I get it. Your brother has probably run off to some dungeon, trying to go adventuring. *rolls eyes*'),
('unnmir_8',	'Or maybe he has gone to one of the bigger cities to the north.'),
('unnmir_9',	'Can\'t say I blame him for wanting to see the world.'),
('unnmir_r',	'Hello again. You should go talk to Nocmar.'),
('unzel_1',	'Hello. I\'m Unzel.'),
('unzel_10',	'Vacor and I used to travel together, but he started to get obsessed with his spell making.'),
('unzel_11',	'He even started to question the Shadow. I knew I had to do something to stop him!'),
('unzel_12',	'I started questioning him about what he was up to, but he just wanted to keep on going.'),
('unzel_13',	'After a while, he became obsessed with the thought of a rift spell. He said it would grant him unlimited powers against the Shadow.'),
('unzel_14',	'So, there was only one thing I could do. I left him and needed to stop him from trying to create the rift spell.'),
('unzel_15',	'I sent some friends to take the spell from him.'),
('unzel_16_1',	'So, here we are.'),
('unzel_16_2',	'So, here we are.'),
('unzel_17',	'What? You killed my four friends? Argh, I feel the rage coming.'),
('unzel_18',	'However, I also realize that all this is the making of Vacor. I\'ll give you a choice now. Choose wisely.'),
('unzel_19',	'Either you side with Vacor and his rift spell, or side with the Shadow, and help me get rid of him. Who will you help?'),
('unzel_2',	'Yes, this is my camp. Lovely place, isn\'t it?'),
('unzel_20',	'Thank you my friend. We will keep the Shadow safe from Vacor.'),
('unzel_21',	'You should go talk to him about the Shadow.'),
('unzel_3',	'Vacor sent you huh? I guess I should have figured he would send someone sooner or later.'),
('unzel_30',	'You killed him? You have my thanks friend. Now we are safe from Vacor\'s rift spell. Here, take these coins for your help.'),
('unzel_4',	'Very well then. Kill me if you must, or allow me to tell you my side of the story.'),
('unzel_40',	'Thank you for your help. Now we are safe from Vacor\'s rift spell.'),
('unzel_5',	'Thank you for listening.'),
('unzel_fight',	'Very well, let\'s fight then.'),
('unzel_msg1',	'Kaverin, my old friend! It\'s good to hear that he is still alive. What is the message?'),
('unzel_msg2',	'Hmmm, yes... Let\'s see... (Unzel opens the sealed message and reads it)'),
('unzel_msg3',	'Yes, this makes sense with what I have seen.'),
('unzel_msg4',	'Thank you for bringing it to me.'),
('unzel_msg5',	'Your help could prove more valuable than you might realize.'),
('unzel_msg6',	'Say hello to my old friend Kaverin the next time you see him, will you?'),
('unzel_msg_r0',	'Hello again. Thank you for your help with defeating Vacor and bringing me the message from Kaverin.'),
('unzel_return_1',	'Welcome back. Did you talk to Vacor?'),
('vacor_10',	'Preposterous, isn\'t it? I was so close to having the power!'),
('vacor_11',	'Oh, the power I could have had. My dear rift spell.'),
('vacor_12',	'Anyway, I was just about to finish the last piece of my rift spell when the bandits came and robbed me.'),
('vacor_13',	'The bandits took my notes for the spell and took off before I could call the guards.'),
('vacor_14',	'After years of work,  I can\'t seem to remember the last parts of the spell.'),
('vacor_15',	'Do you think you could help me locate it? Then I could have the power at last!'),
('vacor_16',	'You will of course be suitably rewarded for your part in me getting this power.'),
('vacor_17',	'I knew I couldn\'t trust... Wait, what? You actually said yes? Hah, well then.'),
('vacor_18',	'Ok, find the four pieces of my rift spell that the bandits took, and bring the pieces to me.'),
('vacor_19',	'There were four bandits, and they all headed south of Fallhaven after I was attacked.'),
('vacor_2',	'What are you, some kind of adventurer? Hm. Maybe you can be of use to me.'),
('vacor_20',	'You should search the southern parts of Fallhaven for the four bandits.'),
('vacor_21',	'Please hurry! I am so eager to open up the rift.. Erm, I mean finish the spell. Nothing odd with that right?'),
('vacor_3',	'Are you willing to help me?'),
('vacor_4',	'A while ago, I was working on a rift spell that I had read about.'),
('vacor_40',	'Oh, you found all four pieces? Hurry, give them to me.'),
('vacor_41',	'Yes, these are the pieces that the bandits took.'),
('vacor_42',	'Now I should be able to finish the rift spell and open up the Shadow rift .. erm I mean open up new possibilities. Yes, that\'s what I meant.'),
('vacor_43',	'The only obstacle between me and continuing my rift spell research is that stupid Unzel fellow.'),
('vacor_44',	'Unzel was my apprentice a while ago. But he started to annoy me with his questions and talk about morality.'),
('vacor_45',	'He said that my spell making was disrupting the will of the Shadow.'),
('vacor_46',	'Bah, the Shadow. What has it ever done for ME?!'),
('vacor_47',	'I shall one day cast my rift spell and we will be rid of the Shadow.'),
('vacor_48',	'Anyway. I have a feeling that Unzel sent those bandits after me, and if I don\'t stop him he will probably send more.'),
('vacor_49',	'I need you to find Unzel and kill him for me. He can probably be found somewhere southwest of Fallhaven.'),
('vacor_5',	'The spell is supposed to, shall we say, open up new possibilities.'),
('vacor_50',	'Bring me his signet ring as proof when you have killed him.'),
('vacor_51',	'Now hurry, I cannot wait much longer. The power shall be MINE!'),
('vacor_6',	'Erm, yes, the rift spell will open things up alright. Ahem.'),
('vacor_60',	'Ha ha, Unzel is dead! That pathetic creature is gone!'),
('vacor_61',	'I can see the blood on your boots. I even got you to kill his minions beforehand.'),
('vacor_62',	'This is a great day indeed. I will soon have the power!'),
('vacor_63',	'Here, have these coins for your help.'),
('vacor_64',	'Now leave me, I have work to do before I can cast the rift spell.'),
('vacor_7',	'So there I was working hard on getting the last pieces together for it.'),
('vacor_70',	'What? He told you his story? You actually believed it?'),
('vacor_71',	'I will give you one more chance. Either kill Unzel for me, and I will reward you handsomely, or you will have to fight me.'),
('vacor_72',	'Bah, lowly creature. I knew I shouldn\'t have trusted you. Now you will die along with your precious Shadow.'),
('vacor_8',	'Then, all of a sudden, a gang of thugs came around and started bullying me.'),
('vacor_9',	'They said they were Messengers of the Shadow, and insisted that I should cease my spell making.'),
('vacor_bah',	'Bah, lowly creature. I knew I shouldn\'t have asked you. Now leave me.'),
('vacor_begin',	'Hello.'),
('vacor_msg1',	'What\'s that in your hands?! ... I recognize that seal!'),
('vacor_msg_10',	'(The map shows a location to the northwest of the former prison of Flagstone.)'),
('vacor_msg_11',	'Now, let\'s see here.'),
('vacor_msg_12',	'(Vacor opens the sealed message and starts reading)'),
('vacor_msg_13',	'Yes ... hm ... Really?! *mumbles* ... yes, indeed ...'),
('vacor_msg_14',	'Thanks kid, you have helped me more than you can possibly understand.'),
('vacor_msg_15',	'HA HA HA!!! THE POWER WILL SOON BE MINE!'),
('vacor_msg_16',	'Thanks for giving me that message, but now please leave me. I have more important things to do than to talk to you.'),
('vacor_msg_3',	'Good, maybe now I can work on my Rift Spell in peace...'),
('vacor_msg_4',	'I must have that document!'),
('vacor_msg_5',	'I must know what they are planning!'),
('vacor_msg_6',	'I have a cache of potions hidden, far to the southwest.'),
('vacor_msg_7',	'Good. Now give me the message.'),
('vacor_msg_8',	'Here, take this map as compensation for your troubles.'),
('vacor_msg_9',	'It will lead you far to the southwest, to one of my secret retreats... where a cache of potions is hidden.'),
('vacor_msg_a1',	'Surely, he didn\'t just give it to you!'),
('vacor_msg_a2',	'So, you killed him? Right?!'),
('vacor_msg_b1',	'How did you get your hands on that document?!'),
('vacor_msg_b2',	'What happened boy?!'),
('vacor_return1',	'Hello again. How is the search for my missing pieces of the rift spell going?'),
('vacor_return2',	'Hello again. Any progress yet?'),
('vacor_return2_2',	'Have you killed Unzel for me yet? Bring me his signet ring when you have killed him.'),
('vacor_return_complete',	'Hello again, my assassin friend. I will soon have my rift spell ready.'),
('vilegard_armorer_1',	'Hello there. Please browse my selection of fine armors and protection.'),
('vilegard_shop_notrust',	'You are an outsider. We don\'t like outsiders here in Vilegard. Please leave.'),
('vilegard_shop_notrust_2',	'I don\'t trust you. You should go see Jolnor in the chapel if you want some sympathy.'),
('vilegard_smith_1',	'Hello there. I heard you helped us here in Vilegard. What can I help you with?'),
('vilegard_smith_fg_1',	'Oh, this is most unexpected but very welcome. I will not question how you acquired these items, but instead express my gratitude for bringing them to me.'),
('vilegard_smith_fg_2',	'Thank you for bringing me these items, they will be most useful to us here in the southern lands, and Vilegard in particular. We rarely get our hands on Feygard items, so these are really welcome.'),
('vilegard_smith_fg_3',	'Instead, you brought them to me. You have my thanks.'),
('vilegard_smith_fg_4',	'Hah, this means that we have another opportunity here. What if you were to deliver some other items to the Feygard patrol instead? Hah, this will really make my day.'),
('vilegard_smith_fg_5',	'I might have something that will do just fine..  Let me just find them.'),
('vilegard_smith_fg_6',	'Here they are. Ha ha, these will do just fine for those deceiving Feygard snobs.'),
('vilegard_smith_fg_7',	'Take these items and deliver them to wherever you were supposed to deliver the items you gave me.'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_1',	'[takes a step back] What.. is.. that? It can\'t be? No. Let me look at it.'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_10',	'The original sword had ornaments of rare crystals, and a blade that was as sharp as nothing else.'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_11',	'I can\'t believe I\'m telling you this. Give. It. Here. Now! It needs to be destroyed!'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_12',	'I.. what? Are you threatening me?'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_13',	'Sigh. You don\'t know what you are getting yourself into, kid.'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_14',	'Regardless, to restore the sword to its former shape, I\'d need some of those crystals that it was adorned with, and those crystals are really hard to come by.'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_15',	'I think they are called Oegyth or something like that. The sword had three of them on its hilt.'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_16',	'Pfft. Run along now, and don\'t threaten anyone else, you hear?'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_17',	'You continue to amaze me. Now, are you really sure that you want to do this? The lives of the people that it has slain will haunt you.'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_19',	'Sigh. Ok, whatever you say. We just need to fit these into there, and sharpen up this bit here.\nThere. It should be almost like it once was.'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_2',	'It has all the markings. But it can\'t be? I don\'t understand.'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_3',	'This thing that you have stumbled upon, my friend. This is the Xul\'viir. A most foul item indeed.'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_4',	'It has been said that King Luthor destroyed the sword so that it would not fall into the wrong hands.'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_5',	'It would seem that either he, or the stories have not been telling the truth.'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_6',	'If restored, anyone wielding it would make their enemies tremble from only the sight of it.'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_7',	'You must destroy it, of course. Here, put it into my smelting pit and we\'ll be rid of it.'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_8',	'Into the smelting pit with it. Good. See how it bubbles and flares? That\'s the lives of countless people thanking you for destroying it.'),
('vilegard_smith_xul_9',	'You can\'t be serious. It needs to be destroyed!'),
('vilegard_tavern_drunk_1',	'Oh look, a lost kid. Here, have some mead kid.'),
('vilegard_villager_1_0',	'Hello. Who are you? You are not welcome here in Vilegard.'),
('vilegard_villager_1_2',	'No, I have certainly not. Even if I had, why would I tell you?'),
('vilegard_villager_2_0',	'By the Shadow, you are an outsider. We don\'t like outsiders here.'),
('vilegard_villager_3_0',	'This is Vilegard. You will find no comfort here, outsider.'),
('vilegard_villager_4_0',	'You look like that other kid that ran around here. Probably causing trouble, as always with outsiders.'),
('vilegard_villager_4_2',	'No, I am sure you are. Outsiders always do.'),
('vilegard_villager_4_3',	'Yes, I know. That\'s why we don\'t want your kind around here. You should leave Vilegard while you still can.'),
('vilegard_villager_5_0',	'Hello there outsider. You look lost, that\'s good. Now leave Vilegard while you can.'),
('vilegard_villager_5_1',	'I don\'t trust you. You should go see Jolnor in the chapel if you want some sympathy.'),
('vilegard_villager_friend',	'Hello there. I heard you helped us common folk here in Vilegard. Please stay for as long as you like friend.'),
('vilegard_villager_friend_1',	'Your brother? No, I haven\'t seen anyone that looks like you. But then again, I never take much notice to outsiders.'),
('waeges_1',	'Welcome friend. What can I do for you?'),
('waeges_2',	'Welcome traveller. I see you are looking at my fine selection of weapons.'),
('wallach',	'Oh, poor old Selgan. Why did it have to be him? I wonder who is next, and I fear for the worst.'),
('warden_prisoner_1',	'That thief? He was caught in the act. Trespassing he was. Trying to get down into the catacombs of Fallhaven church.'),
('warden_prisoner_2',	'Luckily, we caught him before he could get down there. Now he\'ll serve as an example to all other thieves.'),
('warden_prisoner_3',	'Damn thieves. There must be a nest of them around here somewhere. If only I could find where they hide.'),
('wild16_cave',	'The thicket is too dense for you to get through.'),
('woodcutter_0',	'Stupid wasps..'),
('woodcutter_1',	'When travelling, keep to the roads. Veer off course and you might find yourself in danger.'),
('woodcutter_2',	'Stay away from the road to the west, for it leads to Carn Tower. You most certainly do not want to go there.'),
('woodcutter_3',	'Maybe we shouldn\'t have cut down all the trees over there. Those wasps really seem upset.'),
('woodcutter_4',	'I can still feel the sting from those wasps in my legs. Good thing we are done with all the trees now.'),
('woodcutter_5',	'Hello there, welcome to our encampment. You should talk to Hadracor over there.'),
('wrye_mourn_1',	'Shadow help me.'),
('wrye_mourn_2',	'My son! My son is gone.'),
('wrye_mourn_3',	'I don\'t want to talk about it. Not with an outsider like you.'),
('wrye_mourn_4',	'Please leave me.\n\nOh Shadow, watch over me.'),
('wrye_mourn_5',	'My son is dead, I know it! And it\'s those damn guards fault. Those guards with their snobby Feygard attitude.'),
('wrye_mourn_6',	'At first they come with promises of protection and power. But then you really start to see them for what they are.'),
('wrye_mourn_7',	'I can feel it in me. The Shadow speaks to me. He is dead.'),
('wrye_mourn_8',	'Thank you. Shadow watch over me.'),
('wrye_resolved_1',	'Please tell me what happened to him!'),
('wrye_resolved_10',	'Thank you, friend, for finding out what happened to him and telling me the truth.'),
('wrye_resolved_11',	'Oh my poor boy.'),
('wrye_resolved_2',	'I don\'t believe it.'),
('wrye_resolved_3',	'Really?'),
('wrye_resolved_4',	'Attacked?'),
('wrye_resolved_5',	'My dear boy.'),
('wrye_resolved_6',	'He was still alive?'),
('wrye_resolved_7',	'Oh my poor boy. What have I done?'),
('wrye_resolved_8',	'I always thought he shared my view of those Feygard snobs.'),
('wrye_resolved_9',	'And now he is not with us anymore.'),
('wrye_return_1',	'Welcome back. Have you found out anything about my son, Rincel?'),
('wrye_return_2',	'Welcome back. Thank you for your help in finding out what happened to my son.'),
('wrye_story_1',	'It all started with those Feygard royal guards coming here.'),
('wrye_story_10',	'I fear he has died or got hurt somehow. Those bastards probably drove him into his own death.'),
('wrye_story_11',	'*sob* Shadow help me.'),
('wrye_story_12',	'No, but I know it in me that they are. The Shadow speaks to me.'),
('wrye_story_13',	'If you want to help me, please find out what happened to my son, Rincel.'),
('wrye_story_14',	'Please return here as soon as you have found out anything.'),
('wrye_story_15',	'Walk with the Shadow.'),
('wrye_story_16',	'I guess you could ask in the tavern here in Vilegard, or the Foaming Flask tavern just north of here.'),
('wrye_story_2',	'They tried to pressure everyone in Vilegard into recruiting more soldiers.'),
('wrye_story_3',	'The guards would say they needed more support to help squelch the supposed uprising and sabotage.'),
('wrye_story_4',	'My son, Rincel, did not seem to care much for the stories they told.'),
('wrye_story_5',	'I also told Rincel of how bad an idea I thought it was to recruit more people to the Royal Guard.'),
('wrye_story_6',	'The guards stayed a couple of days to talk to everyone here in Vilegard. Then they left. They went to the next town I guess.'),
('wrye_story_7',	'A few days passed, and then suddenly my boy Rincel was gone one day. I am sure those guards managed to somehow persuade him to join them.'),
('wrye_story_8',	'Oh how I despise those evil and snobby Feygard bastards.'),
('wrye_story_9',	'This was several weeks ago. Now I feel an emptiness inside. I know in me that something has happened to my son Rincel.'),
('zombie1',	'Fresh flesh!'),
('zortakb',	'The Zortak will defeat you!');
