('vilegard',	20,	NULL,	'I have talked to Jolnor in the Vilegard chapel. He suggests I help three influential people in order to gain the trust of the people in Vilegard. I should help Kaori, Wrye and Jolnor in Vilegard.',	0),
('vilegard',	30,	2100,	'I have helped all three people in Vilegard that Jolnor suggested. Now the people of Vilegard should trust me more.',	1),
